%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israeli%20embassy%20on%20trivialisation%20of%20Holocaust%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690618373000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102228957%2Cimgsize-24472.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fdisturbed-by-trivialisation-of-holocaust-in-bawaal-israeli-embassy%2Farticleshow%2F102228878.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102228878.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIsrael's%20ambassador%20to%20India%2C%20Naor%20Gilon%2C%20has%20criticised%20Hindi%20movie%20'Bawaal'%20for%20its%20%26quot%3Btrivialisation%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Holocaust%2C%20saying%20it%20contains%20a%20%26quot%3Bpoor%20choice%20of%20terminology%20and%20symbolism%26quot%3B.%20The%20Varun%20Dhawan-starring%20production%20has%20caused%20a%20stir%20for%20using%20the%20Holocaust%20to%20tell%20a%20story%20of%20marital%20discord.%20The%20Simon%20Wiesenthal%20Center%2C%20dedicated%20to%20the%20memory%20of%20Holocaust%20victims%2C%20criticised%20the%20film%20on%20Tuesday%20for%20an%20%26quot%3Boutlandish%20abuse%20of%20the%20Nazi%20Holocaust%20as%20a%20plot%20device%26quot%3B.%20The%20film%20was%20released%20on%2021%20July.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20Makes%20Ex%20Aligarh%20Muslim%20University%20Vice%20Chancellor%20Party%20Vice%20President%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20attempt%20to%20strengthen%20its%20ongoing%20outreach%20among%20Muslim%20Pasmanda%20communities%2C%20the%20BJP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-bjp-rejigs-team-ex-aligarh-muslim-university-head-tariq-mansoor-gets-top-post-4250612%5C%22%3Eon%20Sunday%20appointed%3C%2Fa%3E%20former%20Aligarh%20Muslim%20University%20vice-chancellor%20Tariq%20Mansoor%20as%20one%20of%20its%20vice%20presidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mansoor%20was%20instrumental%20in%20steering%20the%20AMU%2C%20one%20of%20the%20hotbeds%20of%20anti-NRC%20and%20CAA%20protests%2C%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bmiddle%20path%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20later%20closely%20working%20with%20the%20RSS%20on%20its%20project%20to%20promote%20the%20teachings%20of%20Mughal%20prince%20Dara%20Shikoh%20on%20peaceful%20Hindu-Muslim%20coexistence%20that%20was%20in%20contradiction%20to%20his%20brother%20Mughal%20emperor%20Aurangzeb's%20way%20of%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20appointment%20came%20on%20a%20day%20when%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20was%20in%20Rameshwaram%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20to%20launch%20a%20book%20on%20former%20president%20APJ%20Abdul%20Kalam%2C%20also%20one%20of%20the%20icons%20of%20the%20party's%20Pasmanda%20outreach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20has%20been%20continuously%20reaching%20out%20to%20a%20section%20of%20the%20Muslim%20population%20through%20Minority%20Morcha%20meetings%2C%20mostly%20focused%20on%20Pasmanda%20Muslims%2C%20who%20are%20from%20Dalit%20and%20other%20backward%20class%20communities.%20Mr%20Mansoor%20was%20elected%20to%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Legislative%20Council%2C%20the%20fourth%20Muslim%20picked%20by%20the%20BJP%20for%20the%20post%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETariq%20Mansoor%20is%20from%20Aligarh%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20Muslims%20constitute%20roughly%2019%25%20of%20the%20state's%20electorate%2C%20and%20have%20a%20sizeable%20presence%20in%20at%20least%2030%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20out%20of%20which%20they%20play%20a%20major%20role%20in%20deciding%20the%20outcome%20in%2015%20to%2020%20constituencies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20RSS%20functionary%2C%20Mr%20Mansoor%20had%20impressed%20the%20sangh's%20leadership%20by%20his%20work%20on%20the%20Dara%20Shikoh%20project%2C%20by%20effectively%20using%20the%20AMU's%20Persian%20department%20to%20translate%20much%20of%20Shikoh's%20work%20on%20inter-faith%20dialogue%20and%20project%20him%20as%20an%20ideal%20for%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20He%20organised%20seminars%20and%20conferences%20on%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mansoor%2C%20a%20surgeon%2C%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20AMU%20since%20the%201970s%20when%20he%20completed%20his%20MBBS%20degree%20in%20surgery%20from%20the%20university's%20JN%20Medical%20College.%20He%20then%20went%20on%20to%20do%20his%20Master%20of%20Surgery%20(MS)%20degree%20in%201982%20from%20the%20same%20college.%20Apart%20from%20the%20BJP's%20focus%20on%20the%20Pasmanda%20Muslims%2C%20which%20is%20important%20in%20terms%20of%20influence%2C%20the%20RSS%20has%20been%20specifically%20reaching%20out%20to%20Muslim%20academics%2C%20and%20people%20of%20the%20community%20from%20professions%20such%20as%20medicine%2C%20law%2C%20and%20bureaucracy%2C%20to%20make%20a%20difference%20in%20the%20minority%20discourse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamal%20Siddiqui%2C%20head%20of%20the%20BJP's%20Minority%20Morcha%20said%20Mr%20Mansoor%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bnationalist%20Muslim%26quot%3B%20who%20has%20always%20promoted%20the%20ideal%20of%20%26quot%3Bnation%20first.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BHis%20understanding%20of%20the%20fault%20lines%20in%20the%20Muslim%20community%20is%20as%20deep%20as%20his%20knowledge%20about%20the%20country%20and%20its%20history.%20He%20has%20led%20the%20students%20of%20AMU%20on%20the%20right%20path%20and%20prevented%20them%20from%20being%20misled.%20His%20appointment%20will%20help%20the%20party%20to%20expand%20better.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20the%20fourth%20person%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community%20to%20be%20promoted%20to%20the%20Legislative%20Council%20by%20the%20party%20in%20UP%20since%202017%2C%20after%20Bukkal%20Nawab%2C%20Mohsin%20Raza%2C%20and%20Danish%20Azad%20Ansari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mansoor%20was%20the%20AMU%20Vice%20Chancellor%20when%20it%20witnessed%20protests%20against%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%20and%20the%20proposed%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20in%202020.%20He%20was%20then%20criticised%20for%20%26quot%3Bnot%20standing%20up%20for%20students%26quot%3B%20when%20policemen%20allegedly%20barged%20into%20the%20university%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20VC%20of%20Jamia%20Millia%20Islamia%20in%20Delhi%2C%20who%20stood%20by%20the%20students.%20Mr%20Mansoor%20has%2C%20however%2C%20always%20said%20he%20did%20his%20best%2C%20and%20talked%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20welfare%20and%20socio-economic%20justice%20over%20identity%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMansoor%20belongs%20to%20Aligarh%2C%20the%20hub%20of%20Muslim%20politics%2C%20and%20comes%20from%20an%20educated%2C%20middle%20class%20family.%20His%20family%20has%20doctors%20and%20lawyers.%20This%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20Muslims%20we%20want%20to%20work%20with%20to%20take%20the%20nation%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20BJP%20functionary%20from%20UP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhalid%20Anis%20Ansari%2C%20associate%20professor%20from%20Azim%20Premji%20University%2C%20who%20has%20been%20actively%20raising%20issues%20pertaining%20to%20the%20community%20for%20many%20years%2C%20has%20often%20pointed%20out%20that%20Indian%20Muslims%20too%20are%20victims%20of%20caste-based%20stratification%2C%20and%20are%20divided%20into%20three%20main%20classes%2C%20and%20hundreds%20of%20biradaris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Ashraf'%20Muslims%2C%20or%20native%20upper%20caste%20converts%2C%20for%20instance%20Syed%2C%20Sheikh%2C%20Mughal%2C%20Pathan%2C%20etc%20are%20at%20the%20top%2C%20and%20the%20Syed%20biradari%20is%20highly%20revered.%20The%20movements%20against%20the%20Ashraf%20dominance%20have%20been%20led%20by%20the%20'lower'%20ones%20-%20Ajlaf%20(backward%20Muslims)%20and%20Arzal%20(Dalit%20Muslims)%2C%20and%20these%20are%20known%20as%20Pasmandas%2C%20the%20community%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20woo.%20Only%2015%20percent%20of%20the%20community%20come%20from%20these%20upper%20caste%20communities%2C%20while%20the%20rest%20are%20largely%20Pasmanda%20Muslims.%20The%20BJP%20has%20planned%20a%20massive%20Sneh%20Yatra%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20these%20Pasmanda%20Muslims%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuslim%20intellectuals%20and%20opposition%20parties%20have%2C%20however%2C%20said%20this%20was%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20create%20a%20divide%20among%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20and%20that%20often%20the%20Muslim%20victims%20of%20hate%20crimes%20or%20economic%20boycott%20were%20Pasmanda%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690618020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2F36lv01r_tariq-mansoor_625x300_04_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftariq-mansoor-appointed-bjp-vice-president-pasmanda-muslims-jp-nadda-ex-aligarh-muslim-university-vc-who-promoted-dara-shikohs-syncretism-made-bjp-vic-4250713%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20attempt%20to%20strengthen%20its%20ongoing%20outreach%20among%20Muslim%20Pasmanda%20communities%2C%20the%20BJP%20on%20Sunday%20appointed%20former%20Aligarh%20Muslim%20University%20vice-chancellor%20Tariq%20Mansoor%20as%20one%20of%20its%20vice%20presidents.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftariq-mansoor-appointed-bjp-vice-president-pasmanda-muslims-jp-nadda-ex-aligarh-muslim-university-vc-who-promoted-dara-shikohs-syncretism-made-bjp-vic-4250713%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftariq-mansoor-appointed-bjp-vice-president-pasmanda-muslims-jp-nadda-ex-aligarh-muslim-university-vc-who-promoted-dara-shikohs-syncretism-made-bjp-vic-4250713%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftariq-mansoor-appointed-bjp-vice-president-pasmanda-muslims-jp-nadda-ex-aligarh-muslim-university-vc-who-promoted-dara-shikohs-syncretism-made-bjp-vic-4250713%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Eye%20On%202024%20Polls%2C%20BJP%20Makes%20Major%20Changes%20To%20Central%20Team.%20Details%20Here%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBJP%20president%20JP%20Nadda%20rejigged%20the%20list%20of%20the%20party's%20central%20office-bearers%20today%2C%20bringing%20in%20a%20Pasmanda%20Muslim%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20as%20one%20of%20its%20Vice%20Presidents%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Telangana%20unit%20chief%20Bandi%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20was%20appointed%20national%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20dropped%20CT%20Ravi%2C%20a%20leader%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20Dilip%20Saikia%2C%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Assam%2C%20as%20its%20general%20secretaries%2C%20and%20Vinod%20Sonkar%2C%20Harish%20Dwivedi%2C%20both%20Lok%20Sabha%20MPs%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Sunil%20Deodhar%20as%20secretaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERadha%20Mohan%20Agrawal%2C%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20two%20new%20faces%20on%20the%20list%20which%20have%20nine%20general%20secretaries%2C%20seven%20of%20whom%20retain%20their%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20secretaries%20are%20Anil%20Antony%2C%20son%20of%20veteran%20Congress%20leader%20AK%20Antony%2C%20and%20Surendra%20Singh%20Nagar%20and%20Kamakhya%20Prasad%20Tasa%2C%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20UP%20and%20Assam%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nagar%20is%20an%20influential%20Gurjar%20leader%20from%20western%20UP%20while%20Mr%20Tasa%20has%20long%20been%20the%20face%20of%20tea%20tribes%20in%20the%20northeastern%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2013%20vice%20presidents%2C%20nine%20general%20secretaries%2C%20including%20BL%20Santhosh%20as%20the%20in-charge%20of%20the%20organisation%2C%20and%2013%20secretaries%20on%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Union%20minister%20Radha%20Mohan%20Singh%2C%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Bihar%2C%20has%20been%20dropped%20from%20the%20post%20of%20party%20vice%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20BJP%20president%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Laxmikant%20Bajpai%20is%20one%20of%20the%20two%20new%20vice%20presidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Tariq%20Mansoor%20being%20inducted%20as%20a%20party%20vice%20president%2C%20there%20are%20two%20Muslims%20in%20the%20position%20now.%20Kerala%20leader%20Abdulla%20Kutty%20is%20another%20member%20from%20the%20minority%20community%20on%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20appointment%20of%20former%20Aligarh%20Muslim%20University%20(AMU)%20Vice-Chancellor%20Tariq%20Mansoor%2C%20now%20a%20BJP%20MLC%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20is%20being%20seen%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20party's%20overtures%20to%20Pasmanda%20(backward)%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ravi's%20omission%20from%20the%20list%20of%20general%20secretaries%2C%20who%20spearhead%20the%20party's%20policies%20and%20agenda%20nationally%20and%20state-wise%2C%20unlike%20the%20vice%20presidents%20who%20are%20mostly%20figureheads%2C%20is%20being%20seen%20by%20some%20as%20a%20fallout%20of%20the%20BJP's%20big%20defeat%20in%20the%20recent%20assembly%20polls%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four-term%20MLA%20had%20lost%20his%20seat%20in%20a%20close%20fight%20in%20the%20recently%20held%20assembly%20polls%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20party%20leader%20said%20not%20much%20should%20be%20read%20into%20the%20dropping%20of%20several%20office-bearers%2C%20as%20many%20of%20them%2C%20including%20Ravi%2C%20may%20contest%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20and%20will%20be%20focussing%20on%20their%20likely%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20appointment%20of%20Bandi%20Sanjay%20weeks%20after%20his%20removal%20as%20the%20Telangana%20BJP%20president%20is%20a%20signal%20to%20the%20party%20cadres%20that%20he%20remains%20valuable%20to%20the%20national%20leadership%2C%20and%20that%20his%20ouster%20was%20a%20tactical%20call%20taken%20in%20the%20context%20of%20poli