0to%20the%20police%2C%20two%20buses%20collided%20head-on%20at%20around%202%3A30%20am%20on%20NH%2053%20at%20Nandur%20Naka%20flyover%20in%20Malkapur%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20buses%2C%20owned%20by%20a%20company%20named%20Balaji%20Travels%2C%20was%20returning%20to%20Hingoli%20district%20from%20the%20Amarnath%20Yatra%20pilgrimage%2C%20while%20the%20other%2C%20owned%20by%20Royal%20Travels%20company%2C%20was%20heading%20to%20Nashikm%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20buses%20overtook%20the%20other%20at%20Nandur%20Naka%20after%20which%20the%20two%20collided.%20Six%20passengers%20have%20died%2C%20officials%20said.%20Around%2020%20others%20who%20were%20injured%20were%20admitted%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20Buldhana.%C2%A032%20passengers%20with%20minor%20injuries%20have%20been%20given%20first-aid%20at%20a%20nearby%20Gurudwara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20driver%20of%20the%20bus%20returning%20from%20Amarnath%20is%20among%20those%20who%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Highway%20Police%2C%20traffic%20has%20been%20restored%20after%20removing%20the%20bus%20from%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20has%20expressed%20grief%20over%20the%20accident%2C%20and%20announced%20Rs%205%20lakh%20each%20from%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20Relief%20Fund%20as%20compensation%20to%20the%20families%20of%20those%20who%20died.%20The%20Chief%20Minister%20also%20directed%20officials%20to%20provide%20proper%20medical%20treatment%20to%20the%20injured%20at%20government%20expense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20major%20bus%20accident%20in%20the%20Buldhana%20district%20recently.%20On%20July%201%2C%20at%20least%2025%20people%2C%20including%20three%20children%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-bus-fire-live-buldhana-bus-accident-series-of-unfortunate-events-what-led-to-bus-accident-that-charred-25-alive-4168032%5C%22%3Ewere%20burnt%20to%20death%2C%20and%20eight%20ot