7476%2Cimgsize-704535.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fworld-looking-at-india-as-nursery-of-new-possibilities-pm-modi-on-third-anniversary-of-nep%2Farticleshow%2F102227411.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delivering%20the%20inaugural%20address%20at%20the%20%26quot%3BAkhil%20Bhartiya%20Shiksha%20Samagam%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20third%20anniversary%20of%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20said%20various%20global%20universities%20are%20also%20interested%20in%20setting%20up%20their%20campuses%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22PTI%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fworld-looking-at-india-as-nursery-of-new-possibilities-pm-modi-on-third-anniversary-of-nep%2Farticleshow%2F102227411.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20history%20of%20the%20Mar-a-Lago%20club%2C%20the%20site%20at%20the%20center%20of%20Donald%20Trump's%20confidential%20documents%20case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22910%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mar-a-Lago%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c4a77bcf07780019670842%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20this%20aerial%20view%2C%20former%20U.S.%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20Mar-a-Lago%20estate%20is%20seen%20on%20September%2014%2C%202022%20in%20Palm%20Beach%2C%20Florida.%3Cp%3EJoe%20Raedle%2FGetty%20Images)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Mar-a-Lago%20mansion%20was%20originally%20willed%20to%20the%20US%20government%20as%20a%20summer%20home%20for%20the%20president.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhen%20the%20White%20House%20refused%20it%2C%20citing%20high%20maintenance%20costs%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20purchased%20the%20estate.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20iconic%20property%20has%20become%20central%20to%20one%20of%20the%20former%20President's%20criminal%20cases.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%20data-pm-slice%3D%5C%221%201%20%5B%5D%5C%22%3EThe%20Mar-a-Lago%20Club%20has%20frequently%20been%20featured%20in%20the%20news%20cycle%20as%20the%20property%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-key-cases-civil-criminal-investigations-lawsuits-updates-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump's%20confidential%20documents%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20estate's%20political%20connections%20date%20back%20far%20futher%20back%20than%20the%20former%20president's%20embattled%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sprawling%20estate%20was%20first%20opened%20in%201927%20after%20its%20construction%20was%20funded%20by%20the%20heiress%20to%20the%20Postum%20Cereal%20Company%2C%20Marjorie%20Merriweather%20Post%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2022%2F09%2F08%2F1121578102%2Fmar-a-lago-trump-fbi-investigation-history-merriweather-post%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENPR%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20Post%2C%20a%20known%20philanthropist%2C%20frequently%20used%20the%20estate%20to%20host%20events%20for%20elite%20members%20of%20society%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20underprivileged%2C%20according%20to%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20also%20was%20very%20keen%20on%20ensuring%20that%20the%20underprivileged%20were%20invited%20to%20events%20so%20that%20they%20could%20experience%2C%20for%20example%2C%20musical%20concerts%2C%26quot%3B%20journalist%20Michael%20Luongo%20told%20NPR%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20heiress%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20understanding%20of%20the%20importance%20of%20her%20role%20in%20society.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2020-acre%20Mar-a-Lago%20property%2C%20meaning%20%26quot%3BSea%20to%20Lake%26quot%3B%20in%20Spanish%2C%20is%20bordered%20by%20the%20Atlantic%20Ocean%20and%20Lake%20Worth.%20The%20estate%20itself%20is%20over%2037%2C000%20square%20feet%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.maralagoclub.com%2Fhistory%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Mar-a-Lago%20website%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smithsonianmag.com%2Fhistory%2Fhistory-mar-a-lago-180965214%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESmithsonian%20Magazine%3C%2Fa%3E%20reports%20that%20the%20house%20was%20%26quot%3Bgrandiose%26quot%3B%20even%20by%20Palm%20Beach%20standards%20at%20the%20time%20of%20its%20construction.%20At%20its%20finish%2C%20the%20house%20cost%20%247%20million%2C%20the%20equivalent%20of%20nearly%20%24100%20million%20in%20today's%20funds%2C%20per%20NPR.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Smithsonian%20Magazine%2C%20Post%20donated%20the%20house%20to%20the%20government%20upon%20her%20death%2C%20hoping%20it%20would%20serve%20as%20a%20summer%20lodging%20for%20the%20US%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20White%20House%20was%20unwilling%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20Mar-a-Lago's%20expensive%20maintenance%20costs%2C%20Trump%20purchased%20the%20property%20and%20its%20furniture%20in%201985%20for%20only%20%248%20million%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.townandcountrymag.com%2Fstyle%2Fhome-decor%2Fa7144%2Fmar-a-lago-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETown%20%26amp%3B%20Country%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20used%20the%20mansion%20as%20his%20own%20home%20for%20about%2010%20years%2C%20then%20opened%20it%20as%20a%20club%20in%201995.%20While%20in%20office%2C%20he%20referred%20to%20the%20estate%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BWinter%20White%20House.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20purchase%2C%20the%20former%20president%20has%20engaged%20in%20a%20number%20of%20legal%20battles%20over%20the%20property%20with%20the%20state%20of%20Florida.%20Town%20%26amp%3B%20Country%20reported%20that%20he%20sued%20Palm%20Beach%20County%20at%20least%20twice%2C%20once%20for%20%26quot%3Bmalicious%26quot%3B%20direction%20of%20air%20traffic%20over%20Mar-a-Lago%2C%20and%20another%20time%20when%20he%20was%20fined%20for%20having%20an%2080-foot%20flag%20pole%2C%20when%20the%20county%20limit%20is%2042-feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20was%20resolved%20when%20Trump%20took%20office%2C%20since%20air%20traffic%20could%20no%20longer%20move%20over%20Mar-a-Lago%20when%20he%20was%20in%20the%20residence.%20The%20second%20ended%20in%20a%20compromise%3A%20Trump%20agreed%20to%20donate%20%24100%2C000%20to%20veteran's%20charities%20in%20lieu%20of%20paying%20county%20fines%2C%20and%20lowered%20the%20flagpole%20to%2070-feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20in%20office%2C%20Trump%20used%20the%20club%20as%20a%20hub%20for%20business%20meetings%20and%20political%20entertaining%2C%20welcoming%20powerful%20guests%20like%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20and%20Japanese%20Prime%20Minister%20Shinzo%20Abe.%20According%20to%20Town%20%26amp%3B%20Country%2C%20he%20also%20authorized%20a%20missile%20strike%20on%20Syria%20from%20Mar-a-Lago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reporting%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.palmbeachpost.com%2Fstory%2Fnews%2Ftrump%2F2023%2F06%2F12%2Ftrump-mar-lago-florida-membership-cost-melania-celebrity-photos%2F70309203007%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Palm%20Beach%20Post%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0a%20membership%20at%20Mar-a-Lago%20costs%20about%20%24200%2C000%20at%20sign-up%2C%20and%20then%20about%20%2420%2C000%20annually%2C%20though%20the%20club%20is%20so%20exclusive%20that%20only%20members%20know%20the%20exact%20costs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20estate%20is%20central%20to%20the%20case%20against%20Trump%20for%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-a-sup