cleshow%2F102226800.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20on%20Saturday%20took%20over%20the%20investigation%20of%20alleged%20sexual%20assault%20on%20two%20women%20who%20were%20paraded%20naked%20by%20a%20mob%20in%20Manipur%20in%20early%20May.%20The%20CBI%20has%20now%20taken%20over%20the%20FIR%20registered%20by%20Manipur%20Police%20against%20unidentified%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fmanipur-violence-cbi-takes-over-probe-of-women-paraded-naked-and-sexually-harassed-on-video%2Farticleshow%2F102226800.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Shocked%20To%20Find%20Out...%5C%22%3A%20Atishi%20Pulls%20Up%20Top%20Bureaucrat%20On%20Flood%20Relief%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUpset%20at%20delays%20in%20processing%20relief%20aid%20to%20those%20affected%20by%20floods%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Revenue%20Minister%20Atishi%20today%20pulled%20up%20the%20Chief%20Secretary.%20She%20wrote%20to%20the%20top%20bureaucrat%20of%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20asking%20him%20to%20deploy%20all%20officers%20on%20Saturday%20and%20Sunday%2C%20so%20that%20relief%20aid%20can%20be%20transferred%20to%20flood%20affected%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Secretary%20Naresh%20Kumar%20has%20been%20directed%20to%20submit%20a%20status%20report%20to%20the%20Revenue%20Minister%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20by%206%20pm%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtishi%20said%20she%2C%20on%20Friday%20evening%2C%20reviewed%20the%20status%20of%20the%20Rs%2010%2C000%20relief%20aid%20to%20be%20given%20to%20flood%20affected%20citizens%20of%20Delhi%20with%20the%20Principal%20Secretary%20of%20Revenue%20Ashwini%20Kumar%20and%20the%20concerned%20officers%20of%20the%20Revenue%20Department.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20shocked%20to%20find%20that%2C%20out%20of%204%2C716%20families%20who%20were%20staying%20in%20relief%20camps%20during%20the%20flood%2C%20only%20197%20families%20have%20received%20the%2010%2C000%20ex%20gratia%20relief%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Government%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20on%20July%2015%20ordered%20senior%20officials%20to%20monitor%20and%20assist%20the%20District%20Administration%20for%20rescue%2C%20relief%2C%20and%20rehabilitation%20works%2C%20but%20even%20after%2010%20days%20of%20the%20cabinet%20decision%20to%20give%20Rs%2010%2C000%20as%20relief%20to%20affected%20families%2C%20%26quot%3B19%20IAS%20and%2018%20DANICs%20officers%20-%20along%20with%206%20DMs%2C%206ADMs%20and%201%20SDMs%20-%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20process%20this%20relief%20package%20for%20a%20mere%204%2C716%20families%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20the%20number%20of%20officers%20deployed%20for%20flood%20relief%20and%20rehabilitation%2C%20each%20of%20these%20officers%20had%20to%20process%20the%20relief%20for%2070%20families.%20This%20means%20they%20had%20to%20provide%20relief%20to%207%20families%20per%20day%2C%20And%20that%20too%20has%20not%20been%20done.%20Such%20laxity%20is%20absolutely%20shocking%2C%26quot%3B%20Atishi%20wrote%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20is%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20concerned%26quot%3B%20what%20officers%20who%20hold%20crucial%20positions%20in%20various%20departments%20would%20be%20doing%20in%20the%20day-to-day%20tasks%20of%20their%20departments%20if%20they%20are%20showing%20such%20laxity%20in%20times%20of%20emergency%20and%20disaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20swollen%20Yamuna%20river%20had%20recently%20flooded%20several%20areas%20and%20key%20roads%2C%20displacing%20many%20families%20and%20leading%20to%20huge%20loss%20of%20property.%20Water%20had%20reached%20up%20to%20the%20Red%20Fort%20and%20the%20busy%20ITO%20intersection.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690612260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fvuo1qpao_atishi-inspects-the-water-level-of-yamuna-pti-650_650x400_10_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-flood-relief-aid-atishi-aap-shocked-to-find-out-delhi-minister-atishi-pulls-up-top-bureaucrat-on-flood-relief-4250526%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Atishi%20wrote%20to%20the%20top%20bureaucrat%20of%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20asking%20him%20to%20deploy%20all%20officers%20on%20Saturday%20and%20Sunday%2C%20so%20that%20relief%20aid%20can%20be%20transferred%20to%20flood%20affected%20on%20Monday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-flood-relief-aid-atishi-aap-shocked-to-find-out-delhi-minister-atishi-pulls-up-top-bureaucrat-on-flood-relief-4250526%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-flood-relief-aid-atishi-aap-shocked-to-find-out-delhi-minister-atishi-pulls-up-top-bureaucrat-on-flood-relief-4250526%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-flood-relief-aid-atishi-aap-shocked-to-find-out-delhi-minister-atishi-pulls-up-top-bureaucrat-on-flood-relief-4250526%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Have%20To%20Applaud...%5C%22%3A%20Ashwin's%20Interesting%20Take%20On%20Smith's%20%5C%22Non%5C%22%20Run%20Out%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Day%202%20of%20the%20ongoing%20second%20Ashes%20Test%20between%20England%20and%20Australia%20grabbed%20a%20lot%20of%20eyeballs%20after%20Steve%20Smith%20survived%20a%20close%20run-out%20call.%20Smith%20was%20clearly%20out%20of%20the%20crease%20when%20wicketkeeper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jonny%20Bairstow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1551-jonny-bairstow-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJonny%20Bairstow%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20hit%20the%20stumps.%20However%2C%20Smith%20was%20declared%20not%20out%20by%20the%20third%20umpire%2C%20as%20per%20the%20MCC%20rules.%20This%20de