0the%20195-year-long%20wait%20period%20and%20backlog%20which%20has%20left%20them%20in%20a%20constant%20state%20of%20limbo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELed%20by%20Congressmen%20Raja%20Krishnamoorthi%20and%20Larry%20Bucshon%2C%20the%20bipartisan%20group%20of%2056%20lawmakers%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20and%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20Secretary%20Alejandro%20Mayorkas%20requesting%20the%20administration%20take%20executive%20action%20to%20provide%20relief%20to%20high-skilled%20employment-based%20visa%20holders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20letter%2C%20the%20US%20lawmakers%20also%20appealed%20to%20the%20administration%20to%20mark%20all%20dates%20for%20filing%20of%20employment-based%20visa%20applications%20in%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Consular%20Affairs'%20published%20Employment-Based%20Visa%20Bulletin%20as%20%26quot%3Bcurrent%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Green%20Card%2C%20known%20officially%20as%20a%20Permanent%20Resident%20Card%2C%20is%20a%20document%20issued%20to%20immigrants%20to%20the%20US%20as%20evidence%20that%20the%20bearer%20has%20been%20granted%20the%20privilege%20of%20residing%20permanently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20situation%20surrounding%20the%20seven%20per%20cent%20country%20cap%20on%20employment-based%20Green%20Card%20allocation%20is%20causing%20severe%20repercussions%2C%20particularly%20for%20countries%20such%20as%20India%2C%20where%20the%20backlog%20has%20reached%20an%20astonishing%20195%20years%2C%20said%20Foundation%20for%20India%20and%20Indian%20Diaspora%20Studies%20(FIIDS%20USA)%20in%20a%20separate%20appeal%20to%20the%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20backlog%20disproportionately%20affects%20Indian%20tech%20professionals%2C%20who%20constitute%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20the%20highly%20skilled%20STEM%20talent%20and%20US-educated%20graduates%2C%20playing%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20maintaining%20the%20United%20States'%20competitive%20edge%20in%20the%20technology%20industries%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESTEM%20stands%20for%20Science%2C%20Technology%2C%20Engineering%20and%20Mathematics%20(STEM)%20subjects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20backlog%20has%20created%20a%20significant%20barrier%2C%20hindering%20these%20talented%20individuals%20from%20contributing%20meaningfully%20to%20the%20country's%20growth%20and%20innovation%2C%20the%20FIIDS%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20FIIDS%20has%20made%20several%20efforts%20in%20addressing%20the%20concerns%20of%20the%20immigrant%20Indian%20community%2C%20in%20particular%20those%20related%20to%20Green%20Card%20and%20H-1B%20visas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20started%20efforts%20to%20get%20relief%20to%20Indian%20H-1Bs%20who%20are%20stuck%20in%20Green%20Card%20processing.%20We%20launched%20a%20change%20petition%2C%20we%20are%20approaching%20representatives%2C%20various%20other%20organisations%20and%20influencers.%20We%20are%20reaching%20out%20to%20the%20Bureau%20of%20consular%20services%20in%20the%20state%20department%20as%20well%20as%20the%20USCIS%20in%20the%20DHS%20to%20take%20administrative%20action%20to%20make%20the%20priority%20dates%20current%20for%20green%20card%20applicants%2C%26quot%3B%20Khanderao%20Kand%20from%20FIIDS%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20H-1B%20visa%20is%20a%20non-immigrant%20visa%20that%20allows%20US%20companies%20to%20employ%20foreign%20workers%20in%20speciality%20occupations%20that%20require%20theoretical%20or%20technical%20expertise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETechnology%20companies%20depend%20on%20it%20to%20hire%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20employees%20each%20year%20from%20countries%20like%20India%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawmakers%20in%20their%20letter%20said%20that%20marking%20all%20dates%20as%20%26quot%3Bcurrent%26quot%3B%20would%20allow%20employment-based%20applications%20to%20be%20filed%20regardless%20of%20applicants'%20country-based%20priority%20date.%20This%20would%20provide%20relief%20to%20thousands%20of%20individuals%20attempting%20to%20legally%20navigate%20the%20US%20immigration%20system%20and%20could%20potentially%20also%20make%20some%20eligible%20for%20employment%20authorisation%20documents%20to%20change%20jobs%2C%20start%20businesses%2C%20and%20travel%20abroad%20to%20visit%20family%20without%20penalty%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20this%20administrative%20action%2C%20which%20was%20also%20used%20during%20the%20administration%20of%20President%20George%20W%20Bush%2C%20individuals%20are%20left%20in%20a%20constant%20state%20of%20limbo%20and%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20are%20punished%20for%20utilising%20a%20pathway%20of%20legal%20immigration%20by%20being%20forced%20to%20stay%20with%20one%20company%20or%20organisation%20due%20to%20their%20Green%20Card%20status%2C%20they%20said%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20proud%20to%20join%20my%20colleagues%20in%20urging%20the%20Biden%20administration%20to%20address%20bureaucratic%20delays%20in%20our%20legal%20immigration%20system%20that%20are%20holding%20back%20our%20economy%20while%20leaving%20so%20many%20families%20in%20limbo%2C%26quot%3B%20Congressman%20Raja%20Krishnamoorthi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20using%20its%20authority%20under%20the%20existing%20law%2C%20the%20administration%20can%20ease%20this%20burden%20while%20strengthening%20our%20economy%20and%20helping%20to%20create%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongressman%20Bucshon%20said%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20due%20to%20bureaucratic%20red%20tape%20in%20%26quot%3Bour%20nation's%20legal%20immigration%20system%2C%20they%20are%20caught%20in%20the%20visa%20backlog%20and%20don't%20have%20the%20flexibility%20to%20change%20jobs%2C%20start%20businesses%2C%20and%20travel%20abroad%20without%20penalty%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20that%20it's%20important%20for%20the%20administration%20to%20act%20within%20the%20current%20law%20to%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20these%20legal%20immigrants%20to%20navigate%20our%20immigration%20system%20and%20continue%20making%20a%20positive%20contribution%20to%20our%20nation%20and%20our%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20Bucshon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20of%20Immigration%20Voice%20Aman%20Kapoor%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthis%20commonsense%20measure%20proposed%20in%20the%20letter%20by%20Congressmen%20Krishnamoorthi%20and%20Bucshon%20would%20be%20an%20absolute%20game%20changer%20to%20provide%20basic%20human%20rights%20such%20as%20the%20ability%20to%20change%20jobs%20and%20travel%20for%20nearly%20one%20million%20high%20skilled%20immigrants%20whose%20status%20in%20the%20US%20can%20end%20at%20any%20moment%20and%20is%20entirely%20dependent%20upon%20the%20whims%20of%20their%20employer%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20basis%20for%20this%20problem%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bdiscriminatory%26quot%3B%20immigration%20system%20that%20requires%20Indian%20nationals%20to%20have%20to%20wait%20%26quot%3B200%20years%20for%20a%20Green%20Card%20while%20people%20from%20150%20other%20countries%20have%20no%20wait%20at%20all%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Kapoor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20now%20call%20on%20the%20Biden%20administration%20to%20do%20the%20right%20thing%20and%20heed%20the%20call%20of%20this%20rare%20bipartisan%20letter%20and%20give%20high-skilled%20immigrants%20here%20for%20over%20a%20decade%20the%20same%20rights%20to%20work%20and%20travel%20that%20people%20being%20paroled%20into%20the%20US%20for%20the%20first%20time%20just%20this%20week%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20no%20less%20deserving%20of%20basic%20human%20rights%20and%20fairness%20than%20anyone%20else%20and%20we%20hope%20the%20Biden%20administration%20will%20agree%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kapoor%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%2