5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcng.co.tt%2Fwhat-is-cng%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNG%3C%2Fa%3E).%20My%20uncle%20who%20lives%20in%20this%20city%20asked%20me%20to%20come%20here%20and%20try%20my%20luck.%20I%20knew%20how%20to%20drive%20an%20auto%2C%20but%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20competition%20among%20autos.%20There%20were%20fewer%20e-rickshaws%20at%20that%20time%2C%20so%20I%20rented%20one.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28164353%2FAjinesh-explains-the-nuances-of-driving-an-e-rickshaw-in-Ghaziabad.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28164353%2FAjinesh-explains-the-nuances-of-driving-an-e-rickshaw-in-Ghaziabad.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28164353%2FAjinesh-explains-the-nuances-of-driving-an-e-rickshaw-in-Ghaziabad-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665652%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22680%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAjinesh%20explains%20what%20is%20it%20to%20drive%20an%20e-rickshaw%20in%20Ghaziabad.%20Photo%3A%20Debojit%20Dutta%20and%20Srishti%20Gupta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjinesh%20pays%20INR%20300%20as%20rent%20for%20the%20e-rickshaw%20and%20spends%20INR%20210%20on%20the%20rechargeable%20batteries%2C%20which%20he%20swaps%20three%20times%20a%20day%20at%20battery%20swapping%20centres%20across%20the%20city.%20He%20drives%20his%20e-rickshaw%20from%20Ghaziabad%20to%20Noida%20and%20ferries%20passengers%20and%20goods%20too.%20Initially%2C%20this%20was%20profitable%20and%20he%20used%20to%20make%20INR%201%2C500%20a%20day%2C%20but%20as%20more%20people%20started%20driving%20e-rickshaws%2C%20his%20income%20started%20to%20reduce.%20Now%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20his%20workday%2C%20Ajinesh%20is%20left%20with%20the%20same%20INR%20800%E2%80%931%2C000%20that%20he%20used%20to%20make%20driving%20the%20auto%20in%20his%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20e-rickshaws%20posed%20a%20challenge%20to%20the%20auto%20drivers%20when%20they%20started%20taking%20over%20the%20road.%20Now%2C%20the%20e-rickshaw%20drivers%20are%20competing%20among%20themselves%20as%20their%20numbers%20have%20increased%20significantly%2C%20especially%20in%20residential%20areas%20and%20for%20commuting%20to%20and%20from%20the%20metro.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20starts%20driving%20at%208%20am%20and%20finishes%20work%20at%2010%20pm.%20This%2014-hour%20shift%20is%20a%20marked%20increase%20from%20the%20eight%20or%20nine%20hours%20he%20used%20to%20spend%20driving%20his%20auto.%20Ajinesh%20admits%20that%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20get%20enough%20time%20to%20spend%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20their%2011-month-old%20child.%20He%20is%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20only%20earning%20member.%20As%20expenses%20at%20home%20are%20bound%20to%20increase%2C%20he%20wants%20to%20buy%20his%20own%20e-rickshaw%20and%20save%20the%20money%20he%20pays%20in%20rent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20will%20buy%20a%20metal%20rickshaw%2C%20which%20is%20sturdier%20than%20the%20plastic%20variant%20I%20am%20driving%20now.%20They%20are%20available%20for%20INR%201%2C75%2C000%20on%20EMI%20at%20the%20showrooms%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EE-rickshaw%20drivers%20like%20Ajinesh%20say%20that%20the%20interest%20on%20the%20loan%20is%20anywhere%20between%2017%25%20and%2020%25%2C%20which%20is%20a%20substantial%20amount.%20There%E2%80%99s%20also%20a%20down%20payment%20of%20INR%2040%E2%80%9350%2C000.%20As%20many%20people%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20pay%20these%20amounts%2C%20they%20rent%20a%20vehicle.%20The%20Delhi%20government%20is%20providing%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fev.delhi.gov.in%2Fbrands-dealers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epurchase%20incentive%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20INR%2030%2C000%20on%20buying%20e-rickshaws%20and%20a%205%25%20interest%20subsidy%20on%20loans%2C%20but%20this%20is%20limited%20to%20certain%20brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDilip%20Ram%2C%20an%20e-rickshaw%20driver%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Govindpuri%20area%20who%20migrated%20from%20Bihar%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20brands%20in%20the%20market%20now%20and%20the%20government%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20trust%20the%20new%20players.%20There%E2%80%99s%20subsidy%20but%20people%20who%20applied%20for%20it%20have%20been%20waiting%20to%20receive%20those%20for%20two%E2%80%93three%20years%20now.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20avail%20the%20government%20subsidies%2C%20the%20drivers%20must%20have%20documents%20such%20as%20Aadhaar%20card%20and%20electricity%20bills%20for%20residential%20proof%2C%20with%20a%20no-objection%20certificate%20from%20the%20landlord%20in%20case%20of%20rented%20housing.%20Documentation%20is%20often%20a%20challenge%20for%20migrant%20workers.%20Dilip%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20easier%20to%20get%20second-hand%20lead-acid-battery-operated%20rickshaws%20for%20INR%2030%E2%80%9340%2C000.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20the%20lead%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20lithium-ion-battery-run%20vehicle%20that%20Dilip%20drives%20is%20a%20more%20recent%20phenomenon%2C%20e-rickshaws%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.downtoearth.org.in%2Fblog%2Fair%2Fwhy-e-rickshaws-have-emerged-a-winner-in-transition-to-electric-mobility-race-75767%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epowered%20by%20lead%20batteries%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0have%20been%20plying%20the%20Delhi%E2%80%93NCR%20roads%20since%202012%20when%20they%20were%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fsheila-dikshit-asks-transport-department-to-frame-e-rickshaw-policy%2Farticleshow%2F17377492.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaunched%20with%20much%20fanfare%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapps.who.int%2Firis%2Fbitstream%2Fhandle%2F10665%2F259447%2F9789241512855-eng.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoon%20questions%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0started%20being%20raised%20about%20the%20environmental%20and%20health%20impact%20of%20recycling%20lead%20batteries.%20They%20have%20to%20be%20replaced%20as%20they%20run%20out%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.abplive.com%2Fauto%2Fe-rickshaw-battery-management-india-price-fame-state-plan-delhi-assam-schemes-policies-management-of-three-wheels-of-electric-vehicles-revolution-1614798%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eevery%20six%20to%20eight%20months%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2022%2F12%2F12%2Fexactly-how-environment-friendly-are-delhis-e-rickshaws%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENewslaundry%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022%20detailed%2C%20e-rickshaw%20drivers%20sell%20these%20batteries%20to%20dealers%20and%20buy%20new%20batteries.%20However%2C%20the%20dealers%20don%E2%80%99t%20often%20follow%20proper%20recycling%20procedure%2C%20which%20ends%20up%20causing%20pollution%20every%20step%20of%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28164607%2FAn-e-rickshaw-running-on-lead-acid-battery-in-South-Delhi.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28164607%2FAn-e-rickshaw-running-on-lead-acid-battery-in-South-Delhi.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28164607%2FAn-e-rickshaw-running-on-lead-acid-battery-in-South-Delhi-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665653%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22680%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAn%20e-rickshaw%20running%20on%20lead-acid%20battery%20in%20South%20Delhi.%20Photo%3A%20Debojit%20Dutta%20and%20Srishti%20Gupta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202022%2C%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fdelhi-hc-junks-pil-seeking-to-continue-usage-of-traditional-lead-acid-battery-in-e-rickshaws%2F1176419%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebanned%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20registration%20of%20new%20e-rickshaws%20that%20use%20lead%20batteries.%20But%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fgovt-to-register-firs-against-illegal-sale-of-e-rickshaws%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eburgeoning%20black%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20second-hand%20market%2C%20and%20people%20without%20the%20means%20to%20pay%20the%20considerably%20higher%20price%20for%20lithium-run%20rickshaws%20will%20continue%20to%20buy%20lead-battery-operated%20e-rickshaws%20even%20if%20they%20have%20to%20pay%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fghaziabad%2Fe-rickshaws-everywhere-but-most-illegal-in-ghaziabad-drivers-dont-have-permits-either%2Farticleshow%2F97469168.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoccasional%20fine%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECarrying%20the%20load%20alone%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDilip%20says%20that%20if%20the%20drivers%20received%20some%20help%20with%20documentation%2C%20more%20people%20could%20adapt%20to%20the%20change.%20To%20understand%20why%20they%20need%20support%2C%20one%20can%20consider%20the%20example%20of%20Chandan%2C*%20an%20e-rickshaw%20driver%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Govindpuri%20locality.%20He%20could%20not%20avail%20the%20subsidies%20because%20his%20disability%20limits%20his%20movement.%20He%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20knowing%20about%20the%20subsidy%2C%20I%20could%20not%20go%20and%20apply%20for%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20auto%20drivers%2C%20e-rickshaws%20have%20no%20unions%20that%20often%20help%20with%20awareness.%20Bharat%2C%20who%20shifted%20from%20riding%20an%20auto%20to%20buying%20his%20own%20e-rickshaw%20during%20the%20lockdown%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CUnless%20we%20have%20a%20union%2C%20no%20one%20will%20listen%20to%20us.%20You%20need%20a%20union%20to%20take%20an%20issue%20to%20the%20authorities%20and%20even%20to%20have%20a%20conversation%20within%20your%20own%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28164657%2FBharat-in-his-e-rickshaw-explaining-the-need-for-a-union.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28164657%2FBharat-in-his-e-rickshaw-explaining-the-need-for-a-union.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28164657%2FBharat-in-his-e-rickshaw-explaining-the-need-for-a-union-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665654%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22680%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBharat%2C%20in%20his%20e-rickshaw%20in%20Ghaziabad%20explains%20the%20need%20for%20a%20union.%20Photo%3A%20Debojit%20Dutta%20and%20Srishti%20Gupta%2FIndian%20Development%20Review.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharat%20gives%20a%20recent%20example%20of%20how%20a%20group%20intervention%20helped%20resolve%20a%20conflict.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20e-rickshaws%20in%20the%20nearby%20area%20started%20taking%20passengers%20for%20INR%205%20each%20instead%20of%20the%20INR%2010%20that%20we%20usually%20charge.%20They%20were%20carrying%20more%20than%20four%20people%2C%20which%20is%20the%20number%20of%20people%20allowed%20in%20an%20e-rickshaw.%20We%20gathered%20the%20e-rickshaw%20drivers%20in%20the%20area%20and%20called%20a%20meeting%2C%20where%20we%20also%20invited%20the%20police.%20We%20explained%20how%20this%20system%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20beneficial%20for%20any%20of%20us%20in%20the%20long%20run.%20Seventy%20to%2075%25%20of%20them%20agreed%20with%20us%20and%20quit%20the%20practice%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20had%20to%20stop%20eventually.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20despite%20multiple%20efforts%2C%20Bharat%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20convince%20everyone%20about%20setting%20up%20a%20structured%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERaining%20trouble%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20routine%20challenges%20weren%E2%80%99t%20enough%2C%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20e-rickshaw%20drivers%20also%20had%20to%20deal%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dnaindia.com%2Findia%2Freport-delhi-traffic-advisory-overflowing-yamuna-water-causing-mile-long-jams-check-alternate-routes-here-3051541%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20unusual%20monsoon%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20caused%20floods%20and%20waterlogging%20in%20several%20areas%2C%20bringing%20traffic%20to%20a%20standstill.%20This%20affected%20the%20e-rickshaws%20too.%20The%20battery%20compartment%20of%20the%20e-rickshaws%20is%20under%20the%20seats%2C%20and%20when%20the%20water%20seeps%20in%2C%20the%20vehicle%20stops%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28165138%2FDilip-displaying-the-lithium-ion-battery-that-powers-his-ride.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28165138%2FDilip-displaying-the-lithium-ion-battery-that-powers-his-ride.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28165138%2FDilip-displaying-the-lithium-ion-battery-that-powers-his-ride-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665657%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22680%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDilip%20displays%20the%20lithium-ion%20battery%20that%20powers%20his%20ride.%20Photo%3A%20Debojit%20Dutta%20and%20Srishti%20Gupta%2FIndian%20Development%20Review.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20e-rickshaw%20drivers%20had%20to%20give%20up%20driving%20for%20two%E2%80%93three%20days%20during%20heavy%20showers%2C%20there%20were%20others%20who%20found%20ingenious%20hacks%20to%20keep%20going.%20Dilip%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20just%20open%20the%20plug%20that%20connects%20to%20the%20battery%2C%20let%20it%20dry%2C%20and%20put%20it%20back%20on.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECharging%20ahead%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20all%20the%20issues%2C%20Dilip%20says%20e-rickshaws%20make%20more%20sense%20because%20purchasing%20an%20autorickshaw%20costs%20INR%207%E2%80%938%20lakh.%20Drivers%20such%20as%20Dilip%20and%20Bharat%20have%20installed%20EV%20charging%20facilities%20at%20their%20homes.%20It%20costs%20them%20INR%2060%20per%20day%20for%20a%20full%20charge%2C%20which%20takes%20up%20to%20six%E2%80%93eight%20hours%20and%20lets%20the%20vehicle%20run%20for%20100%20km.%20It%20helps%20that%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findia.mongabay.com%2F2022%2F07%2Felectric-vehicle-delhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEV%20charging%20tariff%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0for%20homes%20is%20among%20the%20lowest%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20means%20to%20charge%20at%20home%20can%20use%20the%20multiple%20public%20charging%20stations%20that%20the%20state%20has%20installed.%20However%2C%20here%20they%20have%20to%20pay%20INR%20100%20for%20a%20full%20charge.%20Most%20of%20the%20e-rickshaw%20drivers%20park%20their%20vehicles%20at%20the%20municipality%20parking%20areas%20at%20night%20and%20take%20them%20out%20in%20the%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20cost%20of%20charging%20at%20the%20station%20can%20still%20be%20quite%20high%20for%20many%20people.%20Those%20like%20Ajinesh%2C%20who%20often%20travel%20more%20than%20100%20km%2C%20prefer%20swapping%20their%20batteries%20instead.%20He%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20have%20been%20times%20when%20I%20have%20run%20out%20of%20batteries%20on%20the%20road.%20I%20would%20immediately%20take%20my%20rickshaw%20to%20a%20battery-swapping%20station%20nearby.%20They%20charge%20INR%20150%20for%20the%20first%20battery%20and%20INR%2070%20after%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20push%20for%20EVs%20has%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Fauto%2Fdelhi-to-get-more-ev-charging-battery-swapping-stations-ndmc-vice-chairman-satish-upadhyay-7791913.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egiven%20rise%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20both%20private-%20and%20gove%20rnment-owned%20swapping%20stations.%20However%2C%20there%20have%20been%20safety%20concerns%20regarding%20these%20since%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyourstory.com%2F2023%2F04%2Fbattery-smart-swapping-station-fire-delhi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enews%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20multiple%20such%20places%20catching%20fire%20broke%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fgovernance%2Fwhy-e-rickshaws-are-no-big-draw-for-delhi-drivers-despite-kejriwal-govts-purchase-subsidy%2F915787%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0published%20a%20report%20where%20many%20people%20emphasised%20cost%2C%20fear%20of%20the%20vehicles%20being%20stolen%2C%20and%20lack%20of%20awareness%20about%20government%20initiatives%20as%20reasons%20for%20not%20embracing%20the%20e-rickshaw%20wave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%2C*%20who%20drives%20a%20CNG%20auto%20in%20South%20Delhi%20and%20also%20has%20an%20electric%20auto%20that%20his%20father%20drives%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20difference%20in%20income%20between%20the%20e-rickshaw%20drivers%20and%20auto%20drivers%20for%20me%20to%20want%20to%20make%20the%20shift.%20CNG%20stations%20are%20more%20easily%20available%20than%20EV%20charging%20stations%2C%20which%20are%20mostly%20concentrated%20in%20South%20Delhi.%20I%20might%20be%20paying%20INR%20250%20to%20fill%20the%20tank%2C%20but%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20hours%20to%20charge%20my%20vehicle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CE-rickshaws%20should%20run%20for%20at%20least%20200%20km%20on%20a%20single%20charge%20and%20have%20fast%20charging.%20It%20works%20for%20my%20father%20because%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20go%20very%20far%2C%20but%20he%20struggles%20with%20connecting%20the%20charger%20every%20night.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%3Cem%3ENames%20changed%20to%20maintain%20confidentiality%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20in%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fidronline.org%2F%5C%22%3EIndian%20Development%20Review%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Cem%3ERead%20the%20original%20piece%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fidronline.org%2Farticle%2Flivelihoods%2Fphoto-essay-e-rickshaw-drivers-ferry-indias-electric-dream%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690597855000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28164221%2FFeature-image_An-e-rickshaw-accompanies-daily-life-in-South-Delhi.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fdocumentation-bad-roads-and-charging-costs-challenges-galore-for-delhi-e-rickshaw-drivers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20of%20the%20e-rickshaw%20drivers%20in%20Delhi-NCR%20are%20migrants%20from%20rural%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Bihar%2C%20and%20West%20Bengal%20who%20either%20lack%20awareness%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20unions%20or%20do%20not%20make%20the%20cut%20to%20avail%20Delhi%20government's%20subsidies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fdocumentation-bad-roads-and-charging-costs-challenges-galore-for-delhi-e-rickshaw-drivers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bihar%3A%20Partially%20Disabled%20Bone%20Factory%20Worker%20Lynched%20on%20Suspicion%20of%20Cattle%20Theft%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28201937%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-8.19.30-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBhopal%20(MP)%2FChapra%20(Bihar)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20man%20in%20Bihar%20was%20lynched%20by%20a%20mob%20of%20at%20least%2070%20who%20accused%20him%20of%20smuggling%20beef.%20Fifty-five-year-old%20Zahiruddin%20was%20a%20truck%20driver%20who%20worked%20for%20an%20animal%20bones%20supplier%20and%20byproduct%20manufacturer.%20He%20had%20been%20transporting%20animal%20bones%20%E2%80%93%20an%20essential%20component%20in%20the%20pharmaceutical%20industry%20%E2%80%93%20when%20he%20was%20killed.%20Because%20he%20was%20partially%20disabled%20on%20one%20of%20his%20legs%2C%20he%20could%20not%20run%20from%20the%20mob%2C%20say%20his%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20occurred%20on%20June%2028%2C%20a%20day%20before%20Bakrid%2C%20in%20the%20Paigambarpur%20village%20of%20Saran%20district%20in%20Bihar.%20Saran%20is%20also%20known%20as%20Chhapra%2C%20after%20the%20district%20headquarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZahiruddin%20worked%20for%20what%20is%20commonly%20called%20a%20%E2%80%98bone%20mill%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20a%20factory%20that%20takes%20cattle%20bones%20and%20manufactures%20a%20powder%20that%20is%20essential%20to%20the%20production%20of%20gelatin%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20is%20used%20widely%20in%20the%20pharmaceutical%2C%20cosmetic%20and%20health%20supplements%20industry%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2029%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20Jalalpura%20Police%20Station%20registered%20an%20FIR%20against%20six%20individuals%20%E2%80%93%20Prakash%20Singh%2C%20Sunil%20Singh%2C%20Kallu%2C%20Tribhuvan%20Singh%2C%20Anup%20Singh%2C%20Pramod%20Singh%20%E2%80%93%20and%2030%20unnamed%20others%20under%20Sections%20342%20(punishment%20for%20wrongful%20confinement)%2C%20147%20(punishment%20for%20rioting)%2C%20148%20(rioting%2C%20armed%20with%20a%20deadly%20weapon)%2C%20149%20(unlawful%20assembly)%20and%20302%20(murder)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20named%20accused%2C%20Sunil%20Singh%2C%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3Emukhiya%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20chief%20of%20Paigambarpur%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20the%20Station%20House%20Officer%20of%20Jalalpura%20Police%20Station%2C%20Pintu%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20police%20have%20successfully%20identified%20and%20apprehended%20seven%20previously%20unknown%20suspects%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case.%20However%2C%20there%20are%20innocent%20individuals%20involved.%20The%20police%20have%20obtained%20CCTV%20footage%20as%20part%20of%20the%20investigation.%20We%20are%20awaiting%20supervision%20and%20guidance%20from%20senior%20officers.%20Any%20further%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20orders%20given%20by%20the%20higher%20authorities%2C%E2%80%9D%20informed%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fact-finding%20team%20of%20the%20Association%20for%20Protection%20of%20Civil%20Rights%20visited%20Zahiruddin%E2%80%99s%20house%20in%20Marhaura.%20One%20of%20the%20authors%20of%20the%20report%2C%20Saif%20Ul%20Islam%2C%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Association%20and%20the%20fact-finding%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28201900%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-8.18.49-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28201900%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-8.18.49-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28201900%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-8.18.49-PM-300x160.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28201900%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-8.18.49-PM-1024x544.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665719%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22638%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EZahiruddin%E2%80%99s%20house%20in%20Marhaura.%20Photo%3A%20Saif%20Ul%20Islam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZahiruddin%E2%80%99s%20is%20a%20small%20house%2C%20built%20under%20a%20government%20scheme.%20In%20Marhaura%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20faces%20are%20all%20behind%20the%20%3Cem%3Eghoonghat%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20%3Cem%3Epardah%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20team%20found%20that%20Zahiruddin%E2%80%99s%20sons%20work%20as%20labourers.%20His%20wife%2C%20observing%20the%20Islamic%20mournigng%20period%2C%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Shafaqat%2C%20the%20bone%20mill%20owner%20who%20employed%20Zahiruddin%2C%20conversed%20with%20the%20team.%20Shafaqat%20has%20been%20supporting%20the%20family%20and%20is%20its%20only%20help%20at%20this%20time.%20Zahiruddin%E2%80%99s%20sons%2C%20who%20do%20not%20have%20formal%20education%2C%20also%20appeared%20to%20depend%20heavily%20on%20Shafaqat%2C%20directing%20the%20fact-finding%20team%E2%80%99s%20questions%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShafaqat%20told%20the%20team%20that%20his%20grandfather%20had%20started%20this%20business%20%E2%80%93%20in%201955.%20Since%20then%2C%20his%20have%20been%20running%20it%20smoothly.%20The%20business%20employs%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%2C%20both.%20Since%20inception%2C%20this%20is%20the%20first%20communal%20incident%20that%20any%20of%20its%20workers%20have%20faced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShafaqat%20said%20that%20he%20believes%20that%20those%20who%20killed%20Zahiruddin%20were%20fringe%20elements%20but%20that%20he%20was%20lynched%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20police.%20%E2%80%9CFive%20accused%20in%20mob%20lynching%20have%20pleaded%20guilty%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98A%20raging%20mob%20and%20a%20disabled%20target%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESohail%2C%20the%20younger%20brother%20of%20Shafaqat%2C%20also%20works%20at%20the%20bone%20mill.%20Sohail%20said%20that%20on%20June%2028%2C%20five%20employees%20had%20accompanied%20Zahiruddin%20on%20the%20journey%20to%20Marhaura.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20truck%20driver%20had%20called%20Sohail%20at%20around%20half%20past%20three%20in%20the%20afternoon%2C%20informing%20him%20that%20the%20side%20wing%20of%20their%20vehicle%20has%20broken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28201918%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-8.19.11-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28201918%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-8.19.11-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28201918%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-8.19.11-PM-300x282.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28201918%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-8.19.11-PM-1024x961.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665720%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221126%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20vandalised%20vehicle%2C%20after%20Zahiruddin%E2%80%99s%20death.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESohail%20then%20left%20his%20home%20for%20Paigambarpur%20when%20he%20received%20another%20call%20on%20the%20way%20from%20another%20employees.%20From%20him%2C%20Sohail%20learnt%20that%20local%20youth%20%E2%80%93%20comprising%20mostly%20military%20aspirants%2C%20who%20are%20coloquially%20called%20%E2%80%9Ctrainees%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20had%20gathered%20around%20the%20vehicle.%20The%20caller%20suspected%20that%20they%20had%20been%20alerted%20by%20the%20smell%20of%20bones.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20inspecting%20the%20vehicle%20by%20climbing%20on%20top%20of%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20caller%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20phones%20were%20then%20snatched.%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CKal%20tumhara%20tyohar%20hai.%20Tum%20log%20bahut%20ud%20rahe%20ho.%20Tumhein%20tumhari%20auqat%20dikhate%3C%2Fem%3E%20hai%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20of%20the%20attackers%20had%20allegedly%20told%20the%20bone%20mill%20employees.%20Translated%2C%20the%20line%20means%2C%20%E2%80%9CTomorrow%20is%20your%20festival%2C%20so%20you%20guys%20are%20on%20quite%20a%20high.%20We%20will%20show%20you%20your%20place.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESohail%20stressed%20that%20the%20vehicle%20had%20been%20loaded%20only%20with%20bones%20and%20had%20no%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Sohail%20reached%20Paigambarpur%20with%20a%20companion%20on%20his%20Scorpio%2C%20they%20did%20saw%20a%20raging%20mob%20awaiting%20them.%20They%20parked%20the%20vehicle%20behind%20the%20truck%20and%20dismounted.%20It%20was%20around%20sunset%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20mob%20of%2070%20people%20attacked%20us%20with%20stones.%20They%20broke%20the%20glass%20of%20our%20Scorpio%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sohail%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScared%2C%20Sohail%20and%20his%20companion%20got%20on%20the%20car%20and%20drove%20away%2C%20he%20said.%20The%20other%20five%20employees%20also%20ran%20for%20their%20lives.%20Zahiruddin%2C%20who%20had%20been%20partially%20disabled%20since%20childhood%2C%20could%20not%20run.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20could%20not%20withstand%20the%20brick%20blows%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sohail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Unique%20business%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShafaqat%E2%80%99s%20company%20is%20called%20%E2%80%98Unique%20Bone%20Fertilizers%E2%80%99.%20He%20said%20that%20it%20is%20indeed%20a%20%E2%80%9Cunique%20business%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20earlier%20a%205%25%20sales%20tax%20applicable%20to%20the%20business%20before%20the%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax%20was%20introduced.%20However%2C%20with%20the%20introduction%20of%20GST%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20decided%20to%20promote%20the%20business%20and%20waived%20the%20tax.%20Currently%20it%20is%20nil.%20The%20factory%2C%20licensed%20under%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20Employment%20Generation%20Program%20(PMEGP)%2C%20has%20been%20successfully%20running%20for%20three%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20formation%20of%20this%20bone%20factory%20(bone%20mill)%20was%20overseen%20by%20the%20Task%20Force%20Committee%20under%20the%20supervision%20of%20the%20District%20Magistrate%20who%20also%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20approving%20the%20loan%20for%20the%20PMEGP%20initiative%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shafaqat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20raw%20material%20%E2%80%93%20cattle%20bones%20%E2%80%93%20collected%20from%20slaughterhouses%20and%20dead%20animals%20found%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20serve%20as%20the%20primary%20source%20for%20our%20operations.%20%E2%80%9COur%20core%20process%20involves%20crushing%20these%20bones%20and%20supplying%20them%20to%20gelatine%20factories.%20The%20gelatine%20produced%20is%20further%20sold%20to%20pharmaceutical%20companies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20commented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShafaqat%20manages%20the%20material%20collection%20specifically%20from%20Bihar%2C%20while%20his%20supply%20chain%20extends%20throughout%20India.%20He%20supplies%20to%20renowned%20companies%20like%20Sterling%20Biotech%20and%20India%20Gelatine.%20He%20has%20demanded%20the%20formation%20of%20strict%20laws%20against%20attacks%20on%20employees%20from%20the%20convenor%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Haddi%20Factory%20Union%E2%80%99%2C%20P.D.%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20communal%20incident%20that%20the%20panchayat%20of%20Paigambarpur%20has%20witnessed.%20In%20July%202019%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fthree-lynched-on-suspicion-of-cattle-theft-in-bihars-saran-5837298%2F%5C%22%3Emob%20lynching%3C%2Fa%3E%20killed%20three%20locals%2C%20Bides%20Nat%2C%20Raju%20Nat%2C%20and%20Naushad%20Qureshi.%20The%20mob%20had%20suspected%20them%20of%20cattle%20theft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocals%20told%20the%20fact-finding%20team%20that%20no%20police%20action%20was%20taken%20in%20that%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CZahiruddin%20would%20not%20have%20died%20if%20serious%20action%20was%20taken%20in%20the%20earlier%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20local%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690597835000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28201937%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-8.19.30-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fbihar-partially-disabled-bone-factory-worker-lynched-on-suspicion-of-cattle-theft%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Muslim%20man%20in%20Bihar%20was%20lynched%20by%20a%20mob%20of%20at%20least%2070%20who%20accused%20him%20of%20smuggling%20beef.%20Fifty-five-year-old%20Zahiruddin%20