rticle%2F2023-07%2F18%2Ffull%2F1689648844-2496.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftesla-executives-hold-market-entry-talks-with-india-investment-agency-123072800937_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20Indian%20states%20are%20keen%20to%20woo%20Tesla%20to%20set%20up%20its%20plant%20in%20their%20region%2C%20but%20the%20carmaker%20is%20currently%20focussed%20on%20discussing%20its%20proposal%20with%20the%20federal%20government%20in%20New%20Delhi%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftesla-executives-hold-market-entry-talks-with-india-investment-agency-123072800937_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftesla-executives-hold-market-entry-talks-with-india-investment-agency-123072800937_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftesla-executives-hold-market-entry-talks-with-india-investment-agency-123072800937_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Unhappy%20With%20Data%20Sets%2C'%20Modi%20Govt%20Suspends%20Director%20of%20Institute%20Which%20Prepares%20NFHS%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28214547%2FUntitled-design-21-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20an%20unprecedented%20move%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20suspended%20the%20director%20of%20the%20International%20Institute%20for%20Population%20Sciences%2C%20K.S.%20James%2C%20citing%20an%20irregularity%20in%20recruitment%2C%20sources%20have%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20International%20Institute%20for%20Population%20Sciences%20or%20IIPS%20prepares%20the%20National%20Family%20Health%20Surveys%20and%20does%20other%20such%20important%20exercises%20on%20the%20behalf%20of%20the%20Indian%20government.%20The%20IIPS%20comes%20under%20the%20Union%20health%20ministry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20ministry%20but%20has%20not%20received%20a%20response%20yet.%20The%20story%20will%20be%20updated%20as%20and%20when%20the%20ministry%20responds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20an%20IIPS%20source%20at%20the%20department%20of%20public%20health%20and%20mortality%20studies%20has%20confirmed%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20a%20suspension%20letter%20has%20been%20issued%20and%20that%20further%20details%20would%20come%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESources%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20James%20had%20been%20asked%20by%20the%20government%20to%20resign%20earlier%20as%20the%20government%20was%20not%20happy%20with%20certain%20data%20sets%20that%20came%20up%20in%20the%20surveys%20conducted%20by%20the%20IIPS.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20was%20reluctant%20to%20step%20down%20for%20reasons%20being%20given%3Cspan%3E%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20letter%20of%20suspension%20was%20sent%20to%20James%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20July%2028%2C%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInconvenient%20data%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20a%20government%20that%20believes%20in%20strong%20and%20%E2%80%98positive%E2%80%99%20data%2C%20to%20work%20in%20tandem%20with%20its%20political%20campaign%20for%20electoral%20victories%2C%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20NFHS-5%20had%20thrown%20up%20several%20data%20sets%20inconvenient%20for%20the%20government.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20example%2C%20it%20showed%20that%20India%20was%20nowhere%20close%20to%20being%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fin-eight-years-of-modis-govt-eight-hits-and-misses-in-the-health-sector%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eopen%20defecation%20free%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20a%20claim%20that%20this%20government%2C%20including%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20often%20makes.%20Nineteen%20percent%20of%20households%20do%20not%20use%20any%20toilet%20facility%2C%20meaning%20that%20they%20practice%20open%20defecation%2C%20the%20NFHS-5%20had%20pointed%20out.%20There%20is%20not%20a%20single%20state%20or%20Union%20Territory%2C%20except%20for%20Lakshadweep%2C%20where%20100%25%20of%20the%20population%20has%20access%20to%20a%20toilet%2C%20it%20had%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20NFHS-5%20had%20also%20showed%20that%20more%20than%2040%25%20households%20did%20not%20have%20access%20to%20clean%20cooking%20fuel%20%E2%80%93%20thus%20questioning%20the%20claims%20of%20success%20of%20the%20Ujjwala%20Yojana.%20It%20said%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20more%20than%20half%20the%20population%2C%2057%25%2C%20does%20not%20have%20access%20to%20LPG%20or%20natural%20gas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20NFHS-5%20had%20also%20said%20anaemia%20in%20India%20was%20on%20the%20rise%2C%20and%20there%20have%20been%20some%20recent%20reports%20that%20the%20government%20was%20mulling%20to%20drop%20the%20anaemia%20measurement%20for%20NFHS-6.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERecently%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%2C%20Shamika%20Ravi%2C%20had%20written%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fshamika-ravi-writes-our-national-surveys-are-based-on-faulty-sampling-8799300%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eop-ed%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20claiming%20that%20data%20collection%20for%20NFHS%20and%20other%20such%20surveys%20was%20flawed.%20Her%20article%20was%20criticised%20in%20another%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Findia-population-urban-rural-polulation-growth-difference-population-census-8827669%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eop-ed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20Amitabh%20Kundu%20and%20P.C.%20Mohanan%2C%20published%20in%20the%20newspaper.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJames%20was%20appointed%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Mumbai-based%20institute%20in%202018.%20He%20has%20a%20postdoctoral%20degree%20from%20Harvard%20Centre%20for%20Population%20and%20Development.%20Prior%20to%20joining%20the%20IIPS%2C%20he%20was%20professor%20of%20population%20studies%20at%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20and%20has%20held%20a%20couple%20of%20leadership%20positions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESerious%20questions%20over%20data%20and%20Union%20government%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Union%20government%20has%20been%20in%20the%20news%20often%20for%20a%20very%20uneasy%20relationship%20with%20data.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20trashing%20of%20its%20own%20Consumption%20Expenditure%20Survey%20in%20its%20first%20term%20led%20to%20adverse%20commentary%20and%20raised%20eyebrows.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20withheld%20unemployment%20data%20in%20January%202019%20and%20released%20it%20only%20after%20the%20general%20elections%20were%20over.%20This%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fnsc-members-resign-after-row-over-nsso-employment-report-1548778444218.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eled%20to%20resignations%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eof%20members%20of%20the%20National%20Statistical%20Commission.%20This%20included%20the%20acting%20chairman%20of%20the%20apex%20statistical%20body%2C%20P.C.%20Mohanan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20feeling%20the%20commission%20was%20not%20being%20taken%20seriously%20and%20it%20has%20not%20been%20effective.%20Some%20of%20the%20decisions%20of%20the%20commission%20were%20not%20also%20considered.%20We%20thought%20we%20were%20being%20sidelined.%20Hence%2C%20we%20have%20sent%20our%20resignation%20to%20the%20President%20of%20India%20on%20Monday%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mohanan%20had%20said%20said.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20Mohanan%20and%20the%20other%20member%20J.V.%20Meenakshi%E2%80%99s%20terms%20had%20been%20valid%20till%20June%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20decadal%20Census%20which%20was%20due%20in%202021%2C%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20conducted%20by%20this%20government.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20in%20150%20years%20that%20the%20Census%20has%20been%20postponed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690561699000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28214547%2FUntitled-design-21-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fks-james-nfhs-modi-government-data-sets-iips%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20government%20has%20been%20known%20for%20its%20very%20uneasy%20relationship%20with%20data.%20It%20has%20missed%20a%20deadline%20for%20the%20decadal%20Census.%20Its%20handling%20of%20Consumption%20Expenditure%20series%20and%20then%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20release%20of%20unemployment%20data%20has%20been%20strongly%20criticised%20in%20the%20past.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A167%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fks-james-nfhs-modi-government-data-sets-iips%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20talent%20pool%2C%20govt%20policies%20make%20it%20unique%20for%20semiconductor%20bets%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690561515000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-02%2F16%2Ffull%2F1644977326-8231.jp