0Industry%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20briefing%20for%20the%20Indian%20press%2C%20Japanese%20foreign%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20deputy%20press%20secretary%2C%20Yukiko%20Okano%2C%20said%20the%20%E2%80%9Cview%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20Japanese%20firms%20in%20India%20was%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20would%20like%20to%20see%20a%20more%20predictable%2C%20stable%20and%20transparent%20business%20environment%E2%80%9D%2C%20especially%20related%20to%20regulatory%20and%20tax%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20while%20this%20was%20not%20discussed%20on%20Friday%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20have%20also%20heard%20that%20infrastructure%20challenges%20were%20raised%20in%20the%20past%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Japanese%20spokesperson%20noted%20that%20the%20business%20chambers%20had%20raised%20these%20issues%20with%20Indian%20authorities%20from%20time%20to%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Japanese%20foreign%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20press%20release%20on%20the%20Strategic%20Dialogue%20had%20said%20that%20minister%20Hayashi%20had%20%E2%80%9Crequested%20cooperation%20to%20improve%20the%20investment%20environment%20and%20for%20the%20early%20establishment%20of%20a%20Joint%20Crediting%20Mechanism%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Japanese%20figures%2C%20Japan%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%20third%20largest%20trading%20partner%20and%20fifth%20largest%20investor%20in%202021.%20There%20are%20around%201%2C439%20Japanese%20firms%20having%20presence%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20Japanese%20prime%20minister%20Fumio%20Kishida%E2%80%99s%20visit%20last%20year%2C%20a%20target%20of%20public%20and%20private%20investment%20of%20five%20trillion%20yen%20in%20India%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years%20till%202027%20was%20established.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOkano%20said%20that%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Csteady%E2%80%9D%20progress%20in%20meeting%20the%20target%2C%20but%20added%20that%20both%20sides%20were%20not%20releasing%20yearly%20figures%20on%20that%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E