Unable%20to%20Criticise%20the%20Country%20That%20Has%20Invaded%20Ukraine%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20speaking%20at%20the%20India-Japan%20forum%2C%20Hayashi%20said%20that%20at%20a%20time%20when%20there%20are%20many%20pressing%20challenges%2C%20including%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20aggression%20against%20Ukraine%2C%20Japan%20and%20India%20%E2%80%9Cfully%20share%20the%20necessity%20to%20lead%20the%20world%20to%20cooperation%2C%20rather%20than%20to%20division%20and%20confrontation%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20free%20and%20open%20international%20order%20based%20on%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20is%20key%20to%20realising%20such%20a%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20India%20is%20an%20%E2%80%9Cindispensable%E2%80%9D%20partner%20in%20achieving%20a%20free%20and%20open%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20Hayashi%20said%20%E2%80%9Cfree%E2%80%9D%20means%20each%20country%20is%20free%20to%20make%20decisions%20based%20on%20its%20own%20sovereignty%20and%20%E2%80%9Copen%E2%80%9D%20means%20respect%20for%20principles%2C%20including%20inclusiveness%2C%20openness%20and%20diversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20vital%20that%20we%20refrain%20from%20imposing%20values%20or%20excluding%20certain%20countries.%20This%20concept%20is%20especially%20crucial%20for%20smaller%20countries.%20In%20coordination%20with%20India%2C%20Japan%20intends%20to%20materialise%20such%20a%20concept%20through%20realising%20a%20%E2%80%98Free%20and%20Open%20Indo-Pacific%E2%80%99%20or%20FOIP%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Japanese%20prime%20minister%20will%20be%20back%20in%20India%20for%20the%20second%20consecutive%20year%20to%20attend%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690552839000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28191251%2Fimage-1179.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fduring-japan-fms-visit-japanese-firms-lobby-for-a-