various%20parameters%20to%20split%20your%20capital%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Neha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20built%20an%20app%20for%20borrowers%2C%20agents%2C%20and%20an%20underwriting%20module.%20Neha%20says%20that%20they%20are%20able%20to%20give%20about%2015-16%20per%20cent%20return%20to%20their%2018%2C000%20investors%2C%20and%20have%20disbursed%2010%2C000%20loans.%20India%20P2P%20partners%20with%20last%20mile%20organisations%20like%20Seva%20Mandir%20and%20UNDP%20in%20pockets%20across%20the%20country.%20These%20regions%20include%20Nagaland%2C%20all%20five%20southern%20states%2C%20and%20Maharashtra%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few%2C%20to%20ensure%20that%20women%20everywhere%20are%20able%20to%20access%20credit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20with%20NGOs%20and%20microfinance%20institutions%20(MFIs).%20Most%20loans%20are%20given%20to%20women%20who%20are%20part%20of%20SHGs%2C%20which%20is%20a%20powerful%20structure%20for%20accountability.%20They%20attend%20the%20weekly%20group%20meetings%20of%20SHGs%20to%20ensure%20that%20those%20who%20need%20loans%20are%20given%20loans.%20Our%20loan%20officers%20visit%20the%20borrower%E2%80%99s%20place%20of%20work%20for%20due%20diligence.%20Once%20they%20are%20satisfied%2C%20the%20loans%20are%20disbursed%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20the%20CEO.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20loans%20disbursed%20fall%20between%20Rs%2040%2C000%20and%20Rs%2050%2C000%20on%20an%20average.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIndian%20women%20have%20higher%20credit%20scores%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwomen-india-p2p-1690548462.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22India%20P2P%20caters%20majorly%20to%20women%20borrowers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwomen-india-p2p-1690548462.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwomen-india-p2p-1690548462-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwomen-india-p2p-1690548462-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwomen-india-p2p-1690548462-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwomen-india-p2p-1690548462-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325622%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIndia%20P2P%20caters%20majorly%20to%20women%20borrowers%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeha%20notes%20that%2096%25%20of%20India%20P2P%E2%80%99s%20borrowers%20are%20women.%20The%20biggest%20challenge%20has%20been%20building%20awareness%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20%E2%80%9Crural%20women%20are%20India%E2%80%99s%20best%20asset%20class%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20very%20low%20probability%20that%20your%20income%20will%20be%20affected.%20Women%20are%20the%20best%20asset%20class%20and%20best%20borrowers.%20They%20default%20less.%20The%20default%20rate%20of%20women%20in%20microfinance%20in%20the%20sub%20Rs%201%20lakh%20is%20less%20than%201%25%20in%20India.%20Yet%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20loans%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Neha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20Transunion%20CIBIL%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F316961%2Fbengaluru-entrepreneur-platform-find-jobs-for-women-after-career-maternity-break-herkey%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewomen%20have%20a%20higher%20credit%20score%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20720%20on%20an%20average%20compared%20to%20709%20for%20men.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWomen%20have%20a%20high%20sense%20of%20responsibility.%20They%20pay%20back%20on%20time%20without%20follow%20ups.%20They%20want%20their%20family%20to%20thrive%20and%20prosper.%20Yet%2C%20the%20reject%20rates%20are%20higher%20for%20women%20borrowers.%20They%20are%20asked%20for%20NOCs%20from%20their%20husbands%20or%20fathers%20even%20when%20they%20are%20financially%20independent%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Neha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20says%20that%20there%20is%20a%20very%20high%20demand%20for%20loans%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310452%2Fbengaluru-student-financial-independence-portal-for-domestic-workers-finwin-anaya-jethanandani%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewomen%20who%20run%20small%20businesse%3C%2Fa%3Es.%20She%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20unlock%20capital%20worth%20billions%20of%20dollars%20for%20these%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20India%20has%20to%20become%20a%20prosperous%20and%20more%20equitable%20country%2C%20she%20needs%20to%20give%20women%20more%20credit.%20These%20loans%20help%20families%20overcome%20poverty.%20We%20will%20help%20as%20many%20women%20as%20possible%20to%20do%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESources%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprotium.co.in%2F2023%2F01%2F09%2Fwomen-entrepreneurs-financing-gap%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAs%2520per%25202021%2527s%2520Global%2520Findex%2Cshare%2520against%252015%2525%2520for%2520men.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProtium%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Findicators%2Fwomen-more-credit-conscious-than-men-report%2Farticleshow%2F81389164.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Women%20more%20credit%20conscious%20than%20men%3A%20Report%E2%80%99%3C%