ts%20of%20any%20community%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%2040-minute%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Akhtar%20said%20that%20the%20most%20important%20first%20step%20for%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20to%20place%20a%20draft%20of%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20Without%20such%20a%20draft%20as%20a%20reference%20point%2C%20all%20conversation%20and%20debate%20is%20meaningless.%20This%20draft%2C%20he%20said%2C%20must%20be%20created%20by%20experts%20and%20not%20by%20politicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20time%20to%20seek%20suggestions%20from%20citizens%2C%20communities%2C%20or%20institutions%20should%20come%20after%20such%20a%20draft%20is%20made%20available%2C%20not%20before.%20At%20the%20moment%2C%20this%20is%20happening%20the%20wrong%20way%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkhtar%20further%20said%20that%20while%20it%E2%80%99s%20understandable%20that%20tribals%20like%20the%20Santhals%2C%20the%20Sentinelese%2C%20the%20Jarawas%2C%20or%20those%20in%20Bastar%2C%20the%20Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20Islands%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20are%20excluded%2C%20because%20we%20need%20to%20be%20sensitive%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20effectively%20live%20in%20%E2%80%9Cdifferent%20time%20zones%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20states%20of%20the%20North%20East%2C%20which%20are%20also%20considered%20%5Ba%20home%20to%20the%5D%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20must%20not%20be%20excluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20would%20mean%20the%20end%20of%20the%20concept%20of%20a%20Hindu%20Undivided%20Family%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20end%20of%20restrictions%20on%20marriages%20within%20a%20%3Cem%3Egotra%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20judgments%20on%20inter-caste%20marriages%20by%20khap%20panchayats.%20All%20of%20this%20would%20have%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%2C%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20interview%2C%20about%20the%20intention%20behind%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20advocacy%20of%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%20he%20said%20this%20is%20not%20something%20that%20concerns%20or%20matters%20to%20him.%20As%20he%20put%20it%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20if%20someone%20with%20the%20wrong%20intentions%20does%20the%20right%20thing.%20What%20matters%20is%20the%20right%20thing%20is%20being%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20he%20said%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20whether%20the%20issue%20of%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20is%20being%20raised%20as%20a%20dog%20whistle%20to%20target%20the%20Muslim%20community%20or%20as%20an%20election%20issue%20that%20might%20improve%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20prospects%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20himself%20personally%2C%20he%20said%20that%20he%20has%20personally%20lived%20his%20life%20as%20if%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20applies%20to%20him.%20He%20said%20as%20a%20Muslim%2C%20he%20is%20only%20required%20to%20pay%20alimony%20to%20his%20first%20wife%20for%20four%20months%20but%20he%20has%20consciously%20and%20deliberately%20chosen%20to%20pay%20it%20for%20as%20long%20as%20she%20wanted%20it.%20He%20also%20said%20in%20terms%20of%20inheritance%20and%20his%20treatment%20of%20them%2C%20he%20has%20treated%20his%20son%20and%20daughter%20exactly%20equally%20and%20ensured%20that%20they%20will%20each%20get%20a%2050%25%20share%20of%20what%20he%20leaves%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20interview%2C%20he%20makes%20it%20clear%20that%20for%20him%2C%20the%20most%20important%20issue%20is%20gender%20equality%20and%20absolutely%20no%20discrimination%20against%20women.%20He%20says%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20whether%20this%20is%20delivered%20through%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20or%20in%20some%20other%20way%2C%20but%20this%20remains%20the%20most%20important%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FJqZsQR