d%20every%20year.%20Over%20the%20past%20four%20years%20(since%20FY2017-18)%2C%20this%20number%20has%20been%20increasing%20exponentially.%20As%20of%20May%2031%2C%202023%2C%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcfo.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fleadership%2F67-cfos-in-indian-unicorns-dont-have-prior-startup-experience-study%2F101135512%5C%22%3Ewas%20home%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20108%20unicorns%20with%20a%20total%20valuation%20of%20%24340.80%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20these%2C%2044%20with%20a%20total%20valuation%20of%20%2493%20billion%20were%20born%20in%202021%20and%2021%20with%20a%20total%20valuation%20of%20%2427.00%20billion%20in%202022.%20According%20to%20market%20research%20platform%20Tracxn%2C%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Fentrepreneurship%2Fstory%2Fonly-17-out-of-80-unicorns-in-india-are-profitable-6-start-ups-listed-so-far-373233-2023-03-13%5C%22%3Ehas%20only%2017%20profitable%20unicorns.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EByju%E2%80%99s%2C%20Oyo%2C%20Udaan%2C%20Eruditus%2C%20Unacademy%2C%20Swiggy%2C%20and%20PhonePe%20are%20among%20the%20most%20celebrated%20unicorns.%20What%20is%20common%20to%20most%20of%20them%3F%20They%20have%20all%20run%20up%20huge%20losses%20of%20Rs%201%2C500%20to%204%2C500%20crore%20and%20are%20now%20discovering%20that%20incessant%20venture%20funding%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20sustainable%20proposition.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20two%20ways%20of%20looking%20at%20unicorns.%20For%20some%2C%20they%20are%20a%20sign%20of%20increased%20technological%20prowess%20achieved%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years.%20For%20others%2C%20unicorns%20are%20artificial%20creations%2C%20financial%20bubbles%20waiting%20to%20burst.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20truth%20lies%20somewhere%20in%20between.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20valuation%20of%20unicorns%20is%20quite%20subjective%20because%20they%20are%20in%20the%20earliest%20stage%20of%20their%20growth.%20They%20do%20not%20have%20financial%20records%20or%20performance%20records%20which%20could%20support%20a%20billion-dollar%20valuation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20good%20number%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20would%20have%20been%20a%20negative%20cash%20flow.%20Unicorns%20are%20based%20on%20perceptions%2C%20rather%20than%20knowledge.%20Perception%20is%20based%20on%20the%20assumption%20that%20these%20firms%20have%20a%20strong%20value%20proposition%20that%20their%20competitors%20can%E2%80%99t%20imitate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInvestors%20and%20founders%20have%20collaborated%20smartly%20to%20create%20hype%20about%20these%20startups%2C%20increase%20their%20valuation%2C%20drive%20up%20their%20brand%20value%2C%20list%20them%20on%20the%20bourses%20at%20high%20%2Cand%20exit%20with%20handsome%20profits.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnsuspecting%20market%20investors%20who%20bought%20in%20have%20lost%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%20This%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20surprising%2C%20since%20the%20valuation%20of%20unicorns%20is%20beyond%20the%20comprehension%20of%20average%20investors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMere%20market%20share%20gains%20through%20mindless%20acquisitions%20and%20brash%20spends%20on%20branding%20for%20bolstering%20mindshare%20will%20not%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20avers%20R.%20Ramkumar%2C%20former%20CMD%20of%20Cognizant%20India%2C%20who%20is%20now%20pro%20vice-chancellor%20for%20professional%20learning%20at%20Krea%20University.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Findia-is-generating-many-unicorns-and-decacorns-but-who-gains-from-them%5C%22%3EIndia%20Is%20Generating%20Many%20Unicorns%20and%20Decacorns%2C%20But%20Who%20Gains%20From%20Them%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnicorns%20are%20encountering%20new%20challenges%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fstartup-funding-india-drop-33-percent-2022%5C%22%3Efunding%20winters%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fforeign-investments-into-indian-startup-ecosystem-fall-by-72-in-2023-so-far-report%5C%22%3Evaluation%20markdowns%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Oyo%2C%20Swiggy%2C%20Byju%E2%80%99s%2C%20Meesho%2C%20Eruditus%2C%20PineLabs%2C%20PharmEasy%20and%20the%20like%20are%20hit%20by%20valuation%20markdowns%20%E2%80%93%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20up%20to%2070%25.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20have%20implications%20for%20future%20funding%20rounds%20and%20also%20for%20their%20listing%20plans%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ramkumar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fast-evolving%20trend%20has%20triggered%20panic%20and%20extreme%20cost-cutting.%20The%20disproportionately%20high%20visibility%20of%20unicorns%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20double-edged%20weapon%2C%20as%20their%20precipitous%20fall%20is%20also%20getting%20substantial%20scrutiny.%20They%20have%20to%20now%20demonstrate%20a%20path%20to%20sustained%20revenue%20and%20profit%20growth%2C%20via%20pink%20slips%20and%20cost-cutting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPerception-led%20valuations%20based%20on%20speculative%20market%20tides%20did%20trigger%20a%20kind%20of%20bull%20run%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20over.%20We%20have%20earlier%20seen%20the%20slide%20of%20dotcoms%20and%20e-commerce.%20This%20time%2C%20it%20was%20e-enabled%20services.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CUnreal%2C%20overpriced%20and%20unsustainable%20valuations%20let%20promoters%20and%20interim%20investors%20indulge%20in%20shortcuts%20and%20unethical%20practices%20to%20sustain%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20S.%20Narendran%2C%20a%20former%20executive%20of%20TVS%20Electronics%20and%20a%20data%20scientist.%20%E2%80%9CEntrepreneurs%20are%20lovable%20mavericks%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ramkumar%2C%20and%20they%20become%20the%20fall%20guys.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20about%20the%20boards%20of%20these%20firms%2C%20whose%20members%20guide%20the%20strategic%20investment%2C%20growth%20and%20profitability%20agenda%20of%20start-ups%3F%20%E2%80%9CLike%20coaches%20of%20sporting%20teams%2C%20they%20need%20to%20advise%20on%20building%20all%20the%20muscles%20for%20unicorns%20to%20grow%20gracefully%20and%20become%20proficorns%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ramkumar%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20proficorn%20is%20a%20rarity%20%E2%80%95%20a%20privately%20held%20start-up%20company%20that%20is%20profitable.%20It%20requires%20not%20hype%2C%20but%20strategic%20thinking%20and%20managing%20talent%2C%20leadership%2C%20risk%20and%20stakeholder%20interest.%20Many%20entrepreneurs%20look%20up%20to%20coaching%20support%2C%20so%20boards%20are%20also%20responsible%20for%20the%20misdirected%20focus%20of%20unicorns.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpoor-working-conditions-abusive-practices-byjus-staff-reveal-harsh-work-conditions%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Treated%20Like%20Slaves%2C%20Abusive%20Practices%E2%80%99%3A%20Byju%E2%80%99s%20Staff%20Reveal%20Harsh%20Work%20Conditions%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInternet%20Slide%203.0%20holds%20lessons%20for%20entrepreneurs%20and%20investors.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20cocktail%20of%20greedy%20people%20and%20easy%20money%20seems%20to%20have%20left%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20with%20really%20bad%20hangovers%2C%E2%80%9D%20quips%20the%20former%20head%20of%20a%20leading%20non-bank%20financial%20company%20(NBFC).%20That%20sector%20was%20done%20in%20by%20the%20shenanigans%20of%20unincorporated%20finance%20companies%2C%20which%20used%20advertising%20to%20create%20hype%20in%20the%20early%201990s.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%2C%20NBFCs%20are%20tightly%20regulated.%20The%20troubles%20of%20unicorns%20like%20Byju%E2%80%99s%20suggest%20that%20it%20is%20imprudent%20to%20build%20a%20business%20which%20depends%20on%20incessant%20venture%20funding.%20When%20money%20is%20easy%2C%20these%20startups%20will%20have%20a%20good%20ride%2C%20but%20when%20the%20money%20flow%20dwindles%20%E2%80%93%20as%20it%20is%20happening%20now%20%E2%80%93%20reality%20catches%20up.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnirudh%20Ravi%20Narayanan%2C%20CEO%20and%20co-founder%20of%20electric%20motorcycle%20maker%20Bharat%20New-Energy%20Company%20(formerly%20Boom%20Motors)%2C%20suggests%20that%20companies%20must%20have%20a%20clear%20product-market%20fit%20and%20clear%20unit%20economics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20that%20funding%20has%20dried%20up%2C%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20surprised%20if%20more%20unicorns%20and%20soonicorns%20(soon-to-be%20unicorns)%20exit%20the%20scene%20or%20valuations%20come%20crashing%20down%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECan%20Byju%E2%80%99s%20and%20the%20like%20be%20brushed%20aside%20as%20isolated%20instances%20of%20over-stretch%3F%20They%20show%20that%20hype%20has%20a%20limited%20shelf-life.%20The%20valuation%20game%20just%20isn%E2%80%99t%20enough%20to%20foster%20a%20sustainable%20business%20and%20ensure%20long-haul%20survival.%20It%20is%20time%20that%20unicorns%20woke%20up%20to%20the%20realities%20of%20business%20dynamics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fk-t-jagannathan%5C%22%3EK.T.%20Jagannathan%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20business%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690545644000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28172130%2Fimage-1176.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Funicorns-have-lost-its-time-proficorns-took-the-stage%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20troubles%20of%20unicorns%20like%20Byju%E2%80%99s%20suggest%20that%20it%20is%20imprudent%20to%20build%20a%20business%20that%20depends%20on%20incessant%20venture%20funding.%20When%20money%20is%20easy%2C%20these%20startups%20will%20have%20a%20good%20ride%2C%20but%20when%20the%20money%20flow%20dwindles%2C%20reality%20catches%20up.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Funicorns-have-lost-its-time-proficorns-took-the-stage%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Body%20of%20climber%20missing%20since%201986%20discovered%20on%20melting%20Swiss%20glacier%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690545240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F07%2F768x432%2Fskynews-dna-mountaineer-theodulgletscher_6232913.jpg%3F20230728125917%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbody-of-climber-missing-since-1986-discovered-on-melting-swiss-glacier-12929239%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20remains%20of%20a%20German%20man%20who%20went%20missing%20while%20climbing%20near%20Switzerland's%20iconic%20Matterhorn%20mountain%2037%20years%20ago%20have%20been%20recovered.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1039%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbody-of-climber-missing-since-1986-discovered-on-melting-swiss-glacier-12929239%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fbody-of-climber-missing-since-1986-discovered-on-melting-swiss-glacier-12929239%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fbody-of-climber-missing-since-1986-discovered-on-melting-swiss-glacier-12929239%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20Internet%20Shutdowns%20Hurt%20Women%20More%2C%20Manipur%20Assaults%20Show%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F12082107%2FScreenshot-2023-06-12-at-8.18.56.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20videos%20of%20two%20women%20being%20paraded%20naked%20and%20assaulted%20in%20Manipur%20went%20viral%20last%20week%20on%20social%20media%2C%20the%20remote%20northeastern%20state%20had%20been%20cut%20off%20from%20internet%20access%20for%20nearly%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20took%20place%20on%20May%204%2C%20but%20the%20videos%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Findian-women-set-fire-house-suspect-manipur-sex-assault-case-triggers-outrage-2023-07-21%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20women%20being%20dragged%20and%20groped%20by%20armed%20men%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0before%20what%20onlookers%20say%20was%20a%20gang%20rape%2C%20surfaced%20last%20week.%20Authorities%20said%20they%20are%20investigating%20the%20incident%20and%20have%20arrested%20several%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20imposed%20a%20statewide%20internet%20shutdown%20on%20May%203%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20needed%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Findia-pm-modi-calls-manipur-women-harassment-incident-shameful-2023-07-20%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20curb%20rumours%20and%20disinformation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20quell%20violent%20ethnic%20clashes%20that%20have%20killed%20at%20least%20125%20people%20and%20displaced%20tens%20of%20thousands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20internet%20ban%20in%20the%20state%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eamong%20the%20longest%20in%20India%20to%20date%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20made%20it%20difficult%20to%20alert%20authorities%20and%20journalists%20to%20rights%20violations%2C%20many%20of%20them%20directed%20at%20women%2C%20activists%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20was%20no%20internet%20shutdown%2C%20those%20videos%20would%20have%20surfaced%20over%20two%20months%20ago%20and%20the%20horror%20could%20have%20been%20addressed%20speedily%2C%20and%20other%20similar%20offences%20could%20have%20been%20curbed%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Patricia%20Mukhim%2C%20an%20activist%20and%20editor%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EShillong%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20daily%20headquartered%20in%20Meghalaya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-police-women-video-paraded-naked%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Manipur%20Police%20Were%20Present%2C%20But%20Didn%E2%80%99t%20Help%20Us%E2%80%99%3A%20Women%20in%20Harrowing%20Video%20Tell%20%E2%80%98The%20Wire%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20internet%20shutdown%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20human%20rights%20%E2%80%93%20it%20curtails%20people%E2%80%99s%20freedom%2C%20and%20it%20shuts%20out%20news%20of%20violent%20incidents%20and%20allows%20perpetrators%20to%20carry%20on%20undeterred%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20%3Cem%3EContext%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shutdowns%20also%20have%20an%20%E2%80%9Cadverse%20impact%20on%20women%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20feel%20safe%20and%20restrict%20their%20freedom%20of%20movement%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jayshree%20Bajoria%2C%20an%20associate%20director%20at%20Human%20Rights%20Watch%20in%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20took%20a%20horrific%20video%20of%20violence%20against%20women%20in%20Manipur%20to%20emerge%20on%20social%20media%20for%20the%20authorities%20to%20take%20action.%20This%20shows%20how%20necessary%20the%20internet%20is%20for%20the%20flow%20of%20information%2C%20and%20reporting%20and%20documenting%20abuses%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Manipur%20high%20court%20directed%20the%20state%20government%20to%20restore%20the%20internet%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Climited%20fashion%E2%80%9D%2C%20authorities%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20they%20had%20%E2%80%9Cconditionally%E2%80%9D%20lifted%20the%20ban%20on%20broadband%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20websites%2C%20WiFi%20hotspots%2C%20virtual%20private%20networks%20(VPNs)%20and%20mobile%20internet%20%E2%80%93%20used%20by%20a%20majority%20of%20people%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdigitaldutta%2Fstatus%2F1683814915189145601%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estill%20remain%20blocked%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdverse%20impact%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20had%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.accessnow.org%2Finternet-shutdowns-2022%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%20number%20of%20shutdowns%20in%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0for%20the%20fifth%20successive%20year%20in%202022%2C%20according%20to%20Access%20Now%2C%20a%20digital%20rights%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shutdowns%20%E2%80%93%20including%20during%20protests%2C%20elections%20and%20examinations%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ewere%20often%20imposed%20for%20indefinite%20periods%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.accessnow.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F2022-KIO-Report-final.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewithout%20the%20publication%20of%20shutdown%20orders%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20violation%20of%20a%202020%20judgment%20by%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20top%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAuthorities%20have%20cited%20violence%20as%20part%20of%20the%20rationale%20for%20shutting%20down%20the%20internet.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20to%20show%20internet%20shutdowns%20reduce%20violence%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3Equite%20the%20opposite%2C%E2%80%9D%20Access%20Now%20said%20in%20a%20report%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-violence-reasons-failure-and-solution-q-and-a%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20Behind%20the%20Manipur%20Violence%20and%20Why%20Stopping%20It%20Poses%20a%20Test%20For%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clashes%20in%20Manipur%2C%20which%20borders%20Myanmar%2C%20began%20when%20members%20of%20the%20Kuki%20and%20Naga%20tribal%20groups%20launched%20a%20protest%20on%20May%203%20against%20the%20possible%20sharing%20of%20their%20benefits%20with%20the%20ethnic%20majority%20Meiteis%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20government%20rushed%20thousands%20of%20paramilitary%20and%20army%20troops%20to%20the%20state%20of%203.2%20million%20people%2C%20but%20the%20state%20has%20remained%20tense%20since%2C%20with%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Fwhy-is-indias-manipur-state-grip-ethnic-violence-2023-07-21%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekillings%20and%20other%20incidents%20of%20sporadic%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20restive%20northeast%20region%20is%20among%20the%20least%20developed%20in%20the%20country%2C%20with%20patchy%20internet%20access%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finternetshutdowns.in%2F%5C%22%3Efacing%20frequent%20shutdowns%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20data%20compiled%20by%20the%20Software%20Freedom%20Law%20Center%2C%20a%20digital%20rights%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20more%20services%20are%20digitised%20under%20the%20Digital%20India%20programme%2C%20internet%20shutdowns%20disproportionately%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hrw.org%2Freport%2F2023%2F06%2F14%2Fno-internet-means-no-work-no-pay-no-food%2Finternet-shutdowns-deny-access-basic%3Fref%3Dstatic.internetfreedom.in%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehurt%20rural%20communities%20and%20other%20vulnerable%20groups%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20those%20who%20depend%20on%20social%20welfare%20benefits%2C%20a%20recent%20report%20by%20Human%20Rights%20Watch%20and%20the%20Internet%20Freedom%20Foundation%20(IFF)%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EToll%20on%20women%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20shutdowns%2C%20Indian%20authorities%20also%20frequently%20block%20websites%20and%20issue%20takedown%20orders%20to%20social%20media%20platforms.%20The%20government%20issued%20nearly%207%2C000%20takedown%20orders%20of%20social%20media%20posts%20and%20accounts%20last%20year%20compared%20to%206%2C000%20in%202021%2C%20according%20to%20Access%20Now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20shutdowns%20involve%20blocking%20the%20internet%20on%20mobile%20phones%2C%20which%20is%20how%20most%20of%20the%20population%2C%20particularly%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20access%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20severely%20impacts%20access%20to%20education%20and%20livelihoods%2C%20particularly%20for%20rural%20women%2C%20the%20report%20by%20Human%20Rights%20Watch%20and%20IFF%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Rajasthan%2C%20which%20has%20had%20the%20most%20internet%20shutdowns%20after%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20workers%20in%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20rural%20employment%20guarantee%20programme%20are%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20attendance%20checks%20and%20wage%20payments%20for%20workers%20have%20been%20digitised%2C%20frequent%20internet%20shutdowns%20in%20the%20state%20mean%20that%20many%20women%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20to%20work%2C%20or%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20paid%2C%20said%20Bajoria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20women%20come%20from%20socially%20and%20economically%20marginalised%20households%20%E2%80%A6%20shutdowns%20that%20cut%20off%20internet%20access%20make%20their%20situation%20worse%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Manipur%2C%20the%20shutdown%20means%20that%20women%20cannot%20communicate%20as%20easily%20with%20their%20families%20via%20WhatsApp%2C%20check%20the%20news%2C%20make%20and%20receive%20payments%20on%20the%20phone%2C%20or%20even%20recharge%20their%20mobile%20SIMs%2C%20said%20Ninglun%20Hangal%2C%20who%20works%20with%20development%20non-profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnable%20to%20work%20from%20home%20because%20of%20the%20internet%20ban%2C%20Hangal%20travelled%2013%20hours%20to%20relocate%20to%20neighbouring%20Assam%20state.%20But%20for%20women%20forced%20to%20stay%20back%2C%20conditions%20are%20tough%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20more%20rumours%20and%20misinformation%20circulating%2C%20and%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20way%20to%20check%20or%20clarify%20what%20is%20true%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWomen%20feel%20isolated%20and%20scared%20for%20their%20safety%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20taking%20a%20terrible%20toll.%20More%20cases%20of%20assault%20and%20abuse%20are%20bound%20to%20come%20to%20light%20when%20the%20internet%20is%20restored.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.context.news%2Fdigital-rights%2Findia-internet-shutdowns-hurt-women-more-manipur-assaults-show%3Futm_source%3Dcopy-url%26utm_medium%3Dshare%26utm_campaign%3Dcontext-share%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.context.news%2Fdigital-rights%2Findia-health-data-faces-rising-risk-of-breaches-cyberattacks%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%C2%A0on%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.context.news%2F%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.context.news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3EContext%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%2C%20powered%20by%20the%20Thomson%20Reuters%20Foundation.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690543830000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F12082107%2FScreenshot-2023-06-12-at-8.18.56.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Findias-internet-shutdowns-hurt-women-more-manipur-assaults-show%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIf%20there%20was%20no%20internet%20shutdown%2C%20those%20videos%2