the%20health%20resort%20and%20also%20grants%20permission%20for%20new%20constructions%20after%20getting%20them%20approved%20by%20the%20Building%20Operation%20Controlling%20Authority%20(BOCA)%20of%20the%20PDA%2C%20which%20is%20headed%20by%20the%20Anantnag%20DC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20instead%20of%20acting%20against%20the%20hotelier%2C%20the%20Anantnag%20DC%20amended%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20building%20permission%2C%20and%20the%20PDA%20CEO%20was%20shunted%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20sent%20a%20detailed%20questionnaire%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20(J%26amp%3BK)%20chief%20secretary%20Arun%20Kumar%20Mehta%2C%20seeking%20his%20comments%20on%20the%20alleged%20irregularities%20committed%20by%20the%20administration%20and%20the%20reason%20for%20the%20transfer%20of%20the%20then-PDA%20CEO.%20This%20story%20will%20be%20updated%20if%20and%20when%20he%20responds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20documents%20and%20sources%2C%20permission%20for%20the%20hotel%E2%80%99s%20construction%20was%20approved%20by%20the%20BOCA%20in%20its%2013th%20meeting%20on%20October%206%20and%20October%2025%20last%20year.%20Under%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20permission%20letter%20%E2%80%93%20which%20has%20been%20accessed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20owner%20was%20directed%20to%20complete%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20hotel%E2%80%99s%20first%20hut%20in%20first%20stage%20of%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20%5Bthe%5D%20completion%20of%20one%20hut%2C%20the%20construction%20of%20%5Bthe%5D%20second%20%5Bhut%5D%20shall%20be%20started%20%E2%80%A6%20and%20so%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20states%20while%20stressing%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cregeneration%20of%20the%20natural%20landscape%E2%80%9D%20and%20protection%20of%20the%20environment%20in%20the%20area%2C%20which%20is%20located%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20south%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Lidder%20valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-capt