%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20case%20of%20failure%20the%20same%20shall%20be%20demolished%20by%20the%20Pahalgam%20Development%20Authority%20at%20your%20risk%20and%20cost%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20PDA%20notice%2C%20which%20was%20accessed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27215812%2FHotel-from-far-1024x768.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27215812%2FHotel-from-far-1024x768.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27215812%2FHotel-from-far-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27215812%2FHotel-from-far.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665532%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20construction%20material%20used%20by%20the%20hotelier%20has%20been%20dumped%20on%20the%20pristine%20meadows%2C%20damaging%20the%20natural%20beauty%20of%20the%20area.%20Photo%3A%20Jehangir%20Ali.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2019%2C%20the%20PDA%20CEO%20wrote%20to%20Anantnag%20DC%20Fakhrudin%20Hamid%20seeking%20permission%20for%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20buildings%20%E2%80%9Cin%20case%20the%20applicant%20fails%20to%20follow%20the%20conditions%20laid%20down%20in%20the%20permission%20letter.%E2%80%9D%20The%20letter%20came%20after%20an%20%E2%80%9Cemergency%20meeting%E2%80%9D%20was%20called%20by%20the%20DC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%2C%20accessed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20states%20that%20the%20building%20plan%20of%20the%20hotel%2C%20which%20had%20been%20approved%20by%20the%20BOCA%20(the%20only%20authority%20empowered%20to%20make%20any%20changes%20to%20building%20plans)%2C%20was%20allegedly%20changed%20on%20the%20verbal%20directions%20of%20the%20Anantnag%20DC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%5Bchange%20in%20building%20plan%5D%20needs%20to%20be%20approved%20by%20the%20BOCA%20as%20per%20the%20Development%20Act%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20of%20the%20then-PDA%20CEO%20notes%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20law%20which%20governs%20the%20PDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20the%20BOCA%20didn%E2%80%99t%20meet%20to%20approve%20the%20change%20in%20the%20terms%20of%20permission%20granted%20to%20the%20hotel%20owner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fkashmir-respect-national-symbols-fear%5C%22%3EIn%20Kashmir%2C%20Respect%20for%20National%20Symbols%20Cannot%20Be%20Commanded%20By%20Fear%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20instead%20of%20acting%20on%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20officer%2C%20the%20administration%2C%20which%20is%20run%20directly%20by%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20shunted%20out%20the%20PDA%20CEO%20on%20May%2020%20to%20the%20general%20administration%20department%2C%20which%20is%20considered%20a%20punishment%20posting%2C%20while%20the%20charge%20of%20the%20post%20was%20assigned%20to%20the%20Anantnag%20DC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20contacted%2C%20the%20Anantnag%20DC%20denied%20that%20the%20administration%20had%20resorted%20to%20irregularities%20to%20allow%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20hotel.%20However%2C%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20explain%20the%20reason%20for%20amending%20the%20BOCA%E2%80%99s%20permission%20within%20six%20months%20of%20its%20approval%2C%20and%20directed%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20the%20incumbent%20PDA%20CEO%2C%20Tariq%20Hussain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20can%E2%80%99t%20speak%20on%20the%20matter%20because%20I%20was%20not%20posted%20in%20Pahalgam%20at%20that%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hussain%20said%2C%20while%20refusing%20to%20elaborate%20on%20the%20action%20taken%20against%20the%20hotel%20owner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20J%26amp%3BK%20high%20court%20has%20banned%20construction%20in%20Pahalgam%2C%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98illegal%E2%80%99%20change%20in%20the%20building%20permission%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinfluential%E2%80%9D%20hotel%20owner%20in%20Athnadan%20village%20took%20place%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20administration%20has%20been%20allegedly%20refusing%20permissions%20for%20carrying%20out%20even%20minor%20repairs%20of%20their%20homes%20citing%20the%20court%20ruling%2C%20according%20to%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690542941000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27214048%2FHotel-2-huts.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjk-admin-shunts-official-violations-hotel%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Before%20he%20was%20shunted%20out%2C%20the%20official%20had%20also%20written%20to%20the%20Anantnag%20deputy%20commissioner%20about%20changes%20the%20latter%20made%20to%20the%20hotel's%20construction%20plan%20that%20were%20executed%20in%20contravention%20of%20procedure.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A43%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjk-admin-shunts-official-violations-hotel%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22All%20It%20Takes%20is%20an%20Idea%3A%2018%20Pioneers%2C%2018%20Startups%2C%20%26%20Ideas%20That%20Changed%20Millions%20of%20Lives%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20published%20in%20partnership%20with%20Accenture.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20extraordinary%20idea%20is%20all%20it%20takes%20to%20change%20the%20world.%20This%20is%20the%20theme%20that%20we%20echo%20throughout%20the%20chapters%20of%20our%20audiobook%20%E2%80%94%20brought%20to%20you%20by%20Accenture%20India%20and%20The%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETitled%20%E2%80%98Igniting%20Ideas%20for%20Impact%E2%80%99%2C%20this%20a