rom%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKaran%20Arjun%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(1995)%2C%20a%20semi-erotic%20song%20born%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20phenomenal%20success%20of%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DepYiGd853mQ%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECholi%20Ke%20Peechhe%20Kya%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DepYiGd853mQ%5C%22%3E%20Hai%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKhal%20Nayak%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(1993).%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20glorious%20scene%20where%20Johar%20not%20just%20tells%20us%20about%20his%20disdain%20for%20such%20business-deal%20like%20arranged%20marriage%20meetings%2C%20but%20also%20does%20so%20while%20being%20steeped%20in%20his%20love%20for%20(tacky)%20Hindi%20film%20music.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FWqgXEZkgHrc%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20touted%20as%20the%20blue-eyed%20boy%20of%20the%20young%2C%20mainstream%20Bollywood%20about%2025%20years%20ago%2C%20it%20took%20only%20a%20few%20years%20for%20Johar%E2%80%99s%20limitations%20as%20a%20filmmaker%20to%20start%20showing.%20With%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20Ashutosh%20Gowarikers%20and%20Farhan%20Akhtars%20around%20the%20turn%20of%20the%20millennium%2C%20Johar%E2%80%99s%20ostentatious%20productions%20began%20to%20look%20vacuous.%20It%20resulted%20in%20Johar%20meddling%20with%20his%20natural%20style%20%E2%80%93%20trying%20to%20make%20something%20topical%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20Name%20Is%20Khan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%202009)%2C%20trying%20to%20appease%20a%20younger%20audience%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EStudent%20of%20the%20Year%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%202012)%2C%20making%20a%20relatively%20more%20rooted%20and%20raw%20film%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAe%20Dil%20Hai%20Mushkil%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%202016).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20been%20nearly%20two%20decades%20since%20Johar%20sacrificed%20scale%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20good%20to%20see%20him%20return%20to%20what%20might%20be%20considered%20his%20forte.%20The%20frames%20(by%20cinematographer%20Manush%20Anand)%20are%20wider%2C%20each%20and%20every%20character%20seems%20air-brushed%2C%20the%20lead%20actors%20are%20given%20%E2%80%98professions%E2%80%99%20that%20look%20laughably%20plastic%2C%20regional%20stereotypes%20are%20dialled%20to%20the%20volume%20of%2011%2C%20the%20production%20design%20seems%20to%20have%20the%20budget%20of%20a%20small%20country%E2%80%99s%20GDP.%20It%E2%80%99s%20deliberately%20light-weight%2C%20blindingly%20glossy%2C%20unhealthily%20sweet%20and%20yet%20witty%20when%20you%20least%20expect%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERocky%20Randhawa%20(Ranveer%20Singh)%20%E2%80%93%20the%20scion%20of%20the%20Randhawa%20family%E2%80%99s%20Dhanlaxmi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eladdoo%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20empire%2C%20named%20after%20and%20built%20by%20his%20grandmother%20(Jaya%20Bachchan)%20%E2%80%93%20opens%20the%20film%20with%20a%20charm-offensive%20voiceover%2C%20introducing%20his%20family%20members.%20Bachchan%2C%20who%20has%20spent%20a%20lifetime%20playing%20stoic%2C%20meek%20characters%2C%20is%20refreshingly%20cast%20as%20the%20acidic%20matriarch%20of%20the%20Randhawa%20household.%20Motivated%20by%20her%20quest%20for%20wealth%2C%20and%20disappointed%20by%20her%20husband%20Kanwal%E2%80%99s%20(Dharmendra)%20artistic%20pursuits%2C%20she%20names%20her%20son%2C%20Tijori%20(Aamir%20Bashir)%20and%20rules%20%E2%80%98Randhawa%20paradise%E2%80%99%20(hilariously%20modelled%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20White%20House)%20with%20an%20iron%20fist.%20One%20day%20Kanwal%2C%20who%20after%20an%20accident%20which%20makes%20him%20wheelchair-bound%20and%20suffering%20irregular%20bouts%20of%20amnesia%2C%20starts%20uttering%20a%20name%20%E2%80%98Jamini%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERocky%20looks%20into%20it.%20Sure%20enough%2C%20one%20Google%20search%20later%2C%20he%20finds%20out%20that%20the%20woman%20he%E2%80%99s%20referring%20to%20is%20related%20to%20a%20primetime%20news%20anchor%2C%20Rani%20Chatterjee%20(Alia%20Bhatt).%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELike%20two%20comets%20colliding%20into%20one%20another%2C%20Rocky%20and%20Rani%20meet%2C%20but%20initially%20to%20help%20complete%20the%20love%20story%20of%20Kanwal%20and%20Jamini%20(Shabana%20Azmi)%2C%20Rani%E2%80%99s%20grandmother.%20Seeing%20Rocky%E2%80%99s%20perfectly-chiselled%20torso%20behind%20his%20barely-buttoned%20shirt%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20lust%20at%20first%20sight%20for%20Rani.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28160317%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-3.58.25.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28160317%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-3.58.25.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28160317%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-3.58.25-300x127.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28160317%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-3.58.25-1024x434.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665642%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22509%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20%E2%80%98Rocky%20Aur%20Rani%20Kii%20Prem%20Kahaani.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20inspired%20montage%20of%20recreated%20old%20Hindi%20film%20songs%2C%20Johar%20shows%20Kanwal%20and%20Jamini%20meeting%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20popular%20lovers%E2%80%99%20spots%2C%20only%20to%20show%20another%20love%20story%20blooming%20in%20the%20background.%20As%20the%20elderly%20couple%20sits%20on%20a%20bench%2C%20the%20younger%20couple%20dance%20at%20a%20distance%2C%20almost%20like%20their%20alter-egos.%20Johar%20is%20able%20to%20paint%20the%20love%20stories%20of%20two%20generations%20%E2%80%93%20one%20that%20finds%20solitude%20in%20their%20late%20years%2C%20while%20passions%20rage%20and%20bodies%20intertwine%20without%20much%20thought%20or%20deliberation%20in%20the%20other.%20Dharmendra%20and%20Shabana%20Azmi%20are%20an%20inspired%20choice%20for%20a%20couple%2C%20given%20their%20%E2%80%98schools%E2%80%99%20of%20acting.%20There%E2%80%99s%20something%20sincere%20about%20them%20as%20frail%2C%20longing%20elders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERocky%20and%20Rani%20%E2%80%93%20as%20the%20title%20of%20the%20film%20suggests%20%E2%80%93%20are%20destined%20to%20fall%20in%20love.%20However%2C%20not%20before%20a%20social%20experiment%20that%20includes%20them%20living%20with%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20families%20for%20three%20months%2C%20so%20as%20to%20overcome%20the%20significant%20gap%20in%20their%20cultural%20upbringing.%20Johar%2C%20never%20shying%20away%20from%20a%20joke%20to%20mine%20the%20cultural%20differences%2C%20makes%20a%20joke%20about%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%20being%20referred%20to%20as%20%E2%80%98Dadaji%E2%80%99%20by%20Rocky.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20another%20scene%20Tota%20Roy%20Chowdhury%20%E2%80%93%20playing%20Rani%E2%80%99s%20father%20Chandan%2C%20a%20Kathak%20dancer%20by%20vocation%20%E2%80%94%20is%20shown%20to%20be%20doing%20hand%20movements%20while%20being%20seated%20in%20Rocky%E2%80%99s%20living%20room%2C%20stressing%20upon%20how%20culturally%20refined%20he%20is.%20Seen%20through%20a%20comical%20lens%2C%20it%20does%20disservice%20to%20Roy%20Chowdhury%E2%80%99s%20otherwise%20superbly%20calibrated%20performance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20underneath%20all%20this%20fluff%20and%20humour%20also%20lies%20some%20pointed%20(and%20some%20patronising)%20social%20commentary.%20Johar%20touches%20upon%20the%20casual%20sexism%20in%20the%20Randhawa%20family%2C%20even%20with%20the%20women%20singing%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBpLyDTEw3Z4%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKaanto%20se%20kheech%20ke%20yeh%20aanchal%2C%20tod%20ke%20bandhan%2C%20baandhi%20payal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20in%20front%20of%20their%20oppressors.%20When%20has%20Johar%20ever%20been%20known%20for%20half-measures%3F%20Rocky%20is%20reformed%20from%20his%20toxic%20masculinity%20by%20embracing%20kathak%20because%20of%20Rani%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20and%20the%20Chatterjees%20are%20called%20out%20for%20their%20snootiness%20and%20superiority%20complex%20later%20in%20the%20film.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20most%20of%20the%20progressive%20posturing%20%E2%80%93%20possibly%20inspired%20by%20Ayushmann%20Khurrana%E2%80%99s%20genre%20of%20films%20%E2%80%94%20is%20delivered%20well%2C%20there%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20painful%20detours.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Churni%20Ganguly%2C%20playing%20Rani%E2%80%99s%20mother%2C%20goes%20on%20a%20lengthy%20tirade%20when%20Rocky%20is%20embarrassed%20to%20go%20lingerie%20shopping%20with%20her.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20scene%20between%20Jaya%20Bachchan%20and%20Alia%20Bhatt%20%E2%80%93%20eerily%20similar%20to%20a%20scene%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ECrazy%20Rich%20Asians%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2018)%20where%20Michelle%20Yeoh%20tells%20Constance%20Wu%20%E2%80%9Cyou%20will%20never%20be%20enough%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20that%20ends%20with%20Bhatt%E2%80%99s%20character%20saying%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ekhela%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Ehobe%3C%2Fem%3E%20(the%20game%20is%20on).%E2%80%9D%20This%20is%20the%20oddest%20bit%20of%20appropriation%20from%20Bengal%20politics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKaran%20Johar%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERocky%20Aur%20Rani%20Ki%20Prem%20Kahaani%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20rests%20on%20the%20shoulders%20of%20its%20two%20excellent%20leads.%20Singh%20%E2%80%93%20who%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20miss%20a%20beat%20playing%20a%20%E2%80%9890s%20Govinda%E2%80%93meets%E2%80%93Bittu%20from%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBand%20Baaja%20Baraat%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Efool%20%E2%80%93%20is%20able%20to%20turn%20his%20bratty%20character%20into%20someone%20earnest%20in%20the%20blink%20of%20an%20eye.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBhatt%2C%20looking%20distressingly%20false%20in%20the%20environs%20of%20a%20newsroom%2C%20and%20while%20holding%20a%20glass%20of%20scotch%20at%20one%20of%20her%20family%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Ccultural%E2%80%9D%20evenings%20is%20radiant%20every%20time%20she%E2%80%99s%20around%20Singh.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28160231%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-4.00.40.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28160231%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-4.00.40.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28160231%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-4.00.40-300x127.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28160231%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-4.00.40-1024x434.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665641%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22509%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20%E2%80%98Rocky%20Aur%20Rani%20Kii%20Prem%20Kahaani.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20her%20best%20scenes%20in%20the%20film%20is%20when%20she%E2%80%99s%20thinking%20of%20him%2C%20trying%20to%20douse%20her%20love%20for%20him%20in%20alcohol.%20She%20looks%20at%20her%20colleague%2C%20Soumen%20(Namit%20Das)%20asking%20him%20to%20hug%20her.%20He%E2%80%99s%20a%20little%20taken%20aback%20at%20first%2C%20but%20when%20he%20eventually%20does%20%E2%80%93%20she%20rebuffs%20him.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20tricky%20scene%20where%20Bhatt%20is%20trusted%20to%20navigate%20between%20an%20independent%20woman%20showcasing%20her%20agency%20and%20longing%20for%20someone%20she%20considers%20intellectually%20inferior%2C%20while%20sitting%20beside%20someone%20she%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20fancy%20physically.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJohar%E2%80%99s%20film%20is%20ultimately%20a%20fine%20argument%20for%20everyone%20to%20be%20their%20unapologetic%20selves.%20Like%2C%20in%20a%20scene%2C%20Tota%20Roy%20Chowdhury%20performs%20to%20a%20song%20from%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDevdas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2002)%20at%20a%20Punjabi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esangeet%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20ceremony%20%E2%80%93%20inviting%20sniggers%20for%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20audience.%20The%20scene%20gets%20a%20callback%20later%20in%20the%20film%2C%20when%20Roy%20Chowdhury%20and%20Singh%20perform%20a%20revisionist%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDola%20Re%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It%20appears%20as%20though%20Johar%20has%20finally%20embraced%20his%20reputation%20as%20a%20maker%20of%20fluff%20after%20a%20long%20time%2C%20doubling%20down%20on%20this%20opportunity%20by%20staging%20a%20Durga%20Puja%20of%20Bhansali%20proportions%2C%20a%20funeral%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKabhi%20Khushi%20Kabhie%20Gham%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20proportions%2C%20and%20an%20%E2%80%98intimate%E2%80%99%20wedding%20proposal%20that%20features%20100%20people%20(instead%20of%20500%20background%20dancers%20like%20in%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20songs).%20The%20man%20is%20simply%20incapable%20of%20thinking%20small.%20But%20then%20again%2C%20Johar%20never%20promised%20us%20the%20truth.%20He%20only%20promised%20a%20good%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690541432000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28160424%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-3.58.13.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Frocky-aur-rani-ki-prem-kahaani-karan-johar-ranveer-singh-alia-bhatt-shabana%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20film%20on%20the%20cultural%20gap%20becomes%20an%20occasion%20for%20the%20filmmaker%20to%20subvert%20himself%20without%20losing%20scale%20or%20splendour.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Frocky-aur-rani-ki-prem-kahaani-karan-johar-ranveer-singh-alia-bhatt-shabana%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%20live%3A%20European%20Space%20Agency%20satellite%20crashes%20back%20to%20earth%20in%20guided%20descent%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690540860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F07%2F1600x900%2Fskynews-falling-satellite_6223917.jpg%3F20230719222741%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwatch-live-european-space-agency-satellite-crashes-back-to-earth-in-guided-descent-12929179%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwatch-live-european-space-agency-satellite-crashes-back-to-earth-in-guided-descent-12929179%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwatch-live-european-space-agency-satellite-crashes-back-to-earth-in-guided-descent-12929179%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwatch-live-european-space-agency-satellite-crashes-back-to-earth-in-guided-descent-12929179%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22DGCA%20imposes%20penalty%20of%20Rs%2030%20lakh%20on%20IndiGo%20for%20tail%20strike%20incidents%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690540290000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2020-02%2F11%2Ffull%2F1581417166-7137.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fdgca-imposes-penalty-of-rs-30-lakh-on-indigo-for-tail-strike-incidents-123072800481_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20DGCA%20conducted%20a%20special%20audit%20of%20IndiGo%20to%20examine%20the%20company's%20documentation%20and%20procedures%20pertaining%20to%20operations%2C%20training%2C%20and%20flight%20data%20management%20programme%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fdgca-imposes-penalty-of-rs-30-lakh-on-indigo-for-tail-strike-incidents-123072800481_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fdgca-imposes-penalty-of-rs-30-lakh-on-indigo-for-tail-strike-incidents-123072800481_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fdgca-imposes-penalty-of-rs-30-lakh-on-indigo-for-tail-strike-incidents-123072800481_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Without%20Corrections%2C%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Overseas%20Scholarship%20Could%20Benefit%20Only%20Affluent%20Students%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28125045%2Fimage-1174.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20had%20introduced%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20Scholarship%20for%20Academic%20Excellence%20scheme%2C%20with%20an%20objective%20to%20grant%20students%20from%20the%20economically%20disadvantaged%20community%20in%20the%20state%20an%20opportunity%20to%20pursue%20higher%20education%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20scheme%20was%20launched%20on%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20former%20prime%20minister%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20realising%20his%20vision%20for%20an%20educated%20and%20developed%20India.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20its%20launch%2C%20the%20scheme%20aimed%20to%20help%20200%20students%20from%20the%20state%20to%20pursue%20higher%20education%20at%20prestigious%20institutions%20worldwide%2C%20including%20Oxford%20University%2C%20Harvard%20University%20and%20Stanford%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comprehensive%20plan%20covered%20financial%20assistance%20for%20students%20pursuing%20undergraduate%2C%20postgraduate%2C%20PhD%2C%20and%20postdoctoral%20studies%2C%20with%20the%20state%20government%20fully%20funding%20the%20expenses%2C%20including%20travel%20fares%20and%20tuition%20fees.%20The%20scholarships%20were%20strategically%20allocated%20across%20various%20disciplines%3A%20150%20scholarships%20were%20designated%20for%20students%20pursuing%20humanities%2C%20social%20science%2C%20agriculture%20and%20forest%20science%2C%20nature%20and%20environmental%20science%2C%20and%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%2025%20scholarships%20were%20granted%20to%20students%20pursuing%20management%20and%20business%20administration%2C%20as%20well%20as%20economics%20and%20finance.%20Lastly%2C%2025%20scholarships%20were%20set%20aside%20for%20students%20studying%20pure%20science%20and%20public%20health%20subjects.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20any%20vacancies%20within%20these%20disciplines%2C%20a%20maximum%20of%2015%20candidates%20could%20be%20awarded%20scholarships%20in%20engineering%2C%20related%20science%2C%20medicine%2C%20and%20applied%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20shortly%20after%20the%20scheme%E2%80%99s%20launch%2C%20significant%20revisions%20were%20made%20to%20the%20guidelines%2C%20which%20allowed%20students%20with%20family%20incomes%20above%20Rs%208%20lakh%20to%20apply%20as%20well.%20These%20revised%20guidelines%20applied%20to%20all%20streams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fforeign-universities-india-govt-indifference%5C%22%3EForeign%20Universities%20Regulations%20Reflect%20Modi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Indifference%20to%20Higher%20Education%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20income%20categories%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20guidelines%2C%20students%20were%20categorised%20under%20three%20categories%2C%20based%20on%20their%20family%E2%80%99s%20annual%20income%3A%20up%20to%20Rs%208%20lakh%2C%20between%20Rs%208%20lakh%20and%2025%20lakh%2C%20and%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20and%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20modifications%20unfortunately%20led%20to%20misuse%20of%20the%20scheme.%20As%20reported%20by%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20education%20department%20until%20December%202021%2C%20a%20total%20of%20245%20students%20had%20been%20selected%20for%20the%20scholarship%20scheme%2C%20with%2073%20of%20them%20being%20children%20of%20government%20employees%2C%20including%2014%20IAS%20and%20IPS%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20most%20of%20the%20beneficiaries%20belonged%20to%20the%20two%20new%20income%20categories%20that%20were%20recently%20introduced.%20The%20primary%20objective%20of%20the%20scheme%2C%20as%20emphasised%20by%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%2C%20during%20its%20launch%2C%20was%20to%20provide%20students%20from%20the%20economically%20weaker%20sections%20access%20to%20150%20leading%20global%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20scheme%E2%80%99s%20purpose%20appears%20to%20have%20lost%20its%20essence%20with%20the%20inclusion%20of%20the%20new%20income%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudents%20falling%20within%20the%20income%20bracket%20of%20Rs%208%20lakh%20to%2025%20lakh%20or%20those%20above%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20per%20annum%20could%20feasibly%20afford%20admission%20and%20other%20related%20costs%20on%20their%20own%2C%20making%20them%20less%20in%20need%20of%20support%20from%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lack%20of%20concrete%20action%20taken%20by%20the%20government%20to%20investigate%20the%20selection%20process%20that%20resulted%20in%20the%20inclusion%20of%2073%20students%20with%20government%20servant%20parents%20in%20the%20scheme%20is%20concerning.%20This%20lack%20of%20scrutiny%20gives%20rise%20to%20questions%20about%20the%20transparency%20and%20fairness%20of%20the%20selection%20procedure.%20The%20government%E2%80%99s%20reasoning%20to%20broaden%20the%20income%20criteria%20for%20the%20scheme%20appears%20to%20be%20flawed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20the%20government%20responsibility%20to%20ensure%20proper%20advertising%20and%20widespread%20dissemination%20of%20information%20about%20the%20scheme%20to%20all%20eligible%20students.%20This%20is%20because%20those%20falling%20within%20the%20lower%20income%20brackets%20might%20not%20have%20equal%20access%20to%20information%20compared%20to%20those%20belonging%20to%20the%20higher%20income%20categories.%3Cins%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F26163735%2F2022_9img25_Sep_2022_PTI09_25_2022_000119B-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22749%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F26163735%2F2022_9img25_Sep_2022_PTI09_25_2022_000119B-1.jpg%20749w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F26163735%2F2022_9img25_Sep_2022_PTI09_25_2022_000119B-1-300x181.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-621336%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22453%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAshok%20Gehlot.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20issues%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202023-24%20budget%2C%20the%20government%20increased%20the%20scholarship%20seats%20in%20this%20scheme%20from%20200%20to%20500%20per%20year%2C%20but%20regrettably%2C%20they%20have%20not%20revised%20their%20stance%20on%20the%20income%20criteria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20concerning%20provision%20in%20the%20scheme%20is%20that%20if%20a%20selected%20candidate%20gets%20a%20job%20during%20the%20course%E2%80%99s%20duration%2C%20their%20scholarship%20will%20be%20revoked%2C%20and%20the%20money%20will%20be%20reclaimed.%20This%20provision%20is%20fundamentally%20flawed%2C%20as%20many%20foreign%20countries%20have%20traditions%20of%20allowing%20part-time%20jobs%20for%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20preventing%20students%20from%20engaging%20in%20part-time%20work%2C%20India-bound%20students%20might%20face%20difficulties%20in%20sustaining%20themselves%20in%20a%20foreign%20country%20with%20a%20higher%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20while%20managing%20their%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPart-time%20work%20offers%20valuable%20experiences%2C%20exposing%20students%20to%20the%20culture%20and%20traditions%20of%20the%20host%20country%2C%20which%20can%20be%20an%20invaluable%20asset%20to%20their%20personal%20growth%20and%20development.%20However%2C%20this%20aspect%20has%20seemingly%20been%20disregarded%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20true%20fulfillment%20of%20the%20late%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20vision%20and%20the%20scheme%E2%80%99s%20objectives%20will%20only%20be%20achieved%20when%20it%20prioritises%20economically%20weaker%20individuals%20instead%20of%20assisting%20students%20from%20families%20with%20a%20gross%20income%20exceeding%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20per%20year.%20To%20increase%20awareness%20and%20participation%2C%20the%20local%20education%20department%20can%20conduct%20sessions%20in%20both%20government%20and%20private%20schools%20to%20inform%20students%20about%20the%20scheme%E2%80%99s%20benefits%20and%20application%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20to%20encourage%20students%20belonging%20to%20economically%20disadvantaged%20families%2C%20the%20scheme%20can%20directly%20select%20toppers%20of%20the%20Senior%20Secondary%20School%20Board%20examinations%20from%20the%20poor%20sections%20without%20relying%20on%20a%20lottery%20system.%20This%20approach%20would%20serve%20as%20an%20incentive%20and%20inspire%20more%20students%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20timely%20corrections%20to%20the%20scheme%E2%80%99s%20shortcomings%2C%20there%20is%20a%20risk%20that%20only%20affluent%20students%20will%20benefit%20from%20it.%20To%20avoid%20such%20disparity%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20address%20the%20loopholes%20promptly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBhuvnesh%20Kumar%20and%20Sharad%20Panwar%20are%20fourth%20year%20law%20students%20at%20the%20National%20Law%20University%2C%20Jodhpur.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690540242000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28125045%2Fimage-1174.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Frajasthan-overseas-scholarship-loopholes-benefit-affluent-students%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20purpose%20of%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20Scholarship%20for%20Academic%20Excellence%20appears%20to%20have%20lost%20its%20essence%20with%20the%20inclusion%20of%20new%20income%20categories.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Frajasthan-overseas-scholarship-loopholes-benefit-affluent-students%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22FIFA%20president%20leaves%20Women's%20World%20Cup%20after%20less%20than%20a%20week%20-%20he's%20in%20Tahiti%20instead%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690536780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22h