36_458469909689161_5340703751048844422_n_1080-1690465699-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_313943236_458469909689161_5340703751048844422_n_1080-1690465699-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325403%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22608%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENimal%20Raghavan%20revived%20the%20Peravurani%20Lake%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20after%20Cyclone%20Gaja%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Instagram%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fbeing_nimal%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENimal%20Raghavan%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20cyclonic%20storm%20Gaja%20caused%20massive%20devastation%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20resulting%20in%20over%2045%20fatalities%20and%20damaging%20more%20than%20one%20lakh%20homes.%20Nimal%20Raghavan%2C%20a%20Dubai-based%20software%20developer%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20region%2C%20was%20deeply%20saddened%20by%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20village%20Nadiyam%20was%20one%20of%20the%2090%20villages%20impacted%20by%20the%20cyclone%2C%20resulting%20in%20complete%20destruction%20of%20the%20agricultural%20lands.%20This%20forced%20farmers%20to%20migrate%20to%20cities%20for%20livelihood.%20Interestingly%2C%20while%20many%20of%20Nimal%E2%80%99s%20friends%20decided%20to%20settle%20abroad%20due%20to%20the%20cyclone%E2%80%99s%20havoc%2C%20he%20chose%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F312716%2Fvibha-tripathi-advait-kumar-started-boon-install-drinking-water-atm-in-villages-gurugram%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20different%20path%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20stayed%20in%20his%20homeland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2035%20years%20old%2C%20Nimal%20left%20his%20job%20in%20Dubai%20to%20restore%20his%20hometown%E2%80%99s%20former%20prosperity.%20His%20first%20priority%20was%20reviving%20Peravurani%20lake%2C%20which%20could%20irrigate%20more%20than%206%2C000%20acres%20of%20farmland.%20The%20project%20required%20Rs%2032%20lakh%2C%20and%20with%20the%20help%20of%20like-minded%20volunteers%2C%20he%20planted%2025%2C000%20saplings%20across%20the%20Kaveri%20delta%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20social%20media%20campaign%20%23BounceBackDelta%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20help%20all%20those%20affected%20by%20the%20cyclone%20with%20clothes%2C%20groceries%2C%20household%20necessities%2C%20and%20money.%20The%20other%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F303262%2Fiit-roorkee-professor-technology-to-remove-arsenic-contamination-purify-drinking-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprojects%20taken%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20his%20team%20include%20the%20Miyawaki%20plantation%2C%20a%20mangrove%20forest%20plantation%2C%20as%20well%20as%20rainwater%20harvesting%20and%20water%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20far%2C%20more%20than%2040%20lakh%20people%20have%20benefited%20from%20restored%20water%20bodies%2C%20which%20have%20helped%20them%20access%20fresh%20drinking%20water%2C%20irrigate%20agricultural%20land%2C%20and%20earn%20a%20livelihood.%20Together%2C%20we%20have%20restored%20a%20total%20of%20118%20water%20bodies%20across%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Babita%20Rajput%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20847px)%20100vw%2C%20847px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FBabita-1690465852.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22847%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Babita%20Rajput%20formed%20a%20group%20of%20200%20women%20in%20her%20village%20of%20Agrotha%20to%20tackle%20drought%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploa