have%20tie-ins%20with%20six%20other%20NGOs%20in%20and%20around%20Delhi%20NCR%20region%20who%20help%20us%20reach%20the%20remotest%20person%20who%20may%20need%20help.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20I%20was%20a%20child%2C%20my%20parents%20and%20teachers%20have%20motivated%20me%20to%20find%20solutions%20to%20societal%20problems.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20always%20understood%20that%20regardless%20of%20my%20chosen%20career%2C%20improving%20society%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F165682%2Famazon-india-inclusive-workplace-hearing-disability%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eensuring%20inclusivity%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewill%20remain%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tarini.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20for%20the%20future%2C%20we%20want%20to%20help%20neurodivergent%20entrepreneurs%20get%20funding%20and%20help%20them%20boost%20their%20ventures.%20This%20will%20not%20only%20uplift%20them%20but%20also%20uplift%20the%20people%20of%20their%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20wish%20to%20volunteer%20with%20Tarini%2C%20you%20can%20reach%20her%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnaisubah.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enaisubah.org.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690466088000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FTarini-malhotra-3-1690465096.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D325345%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Diana%20Award-recipient%20from%20Delhi%2C%20Tarini%20Malhotra%20(18)%20started%20Nai%20Subah%20Foundation%20when%20she%20was%20just%2016%20to%20help%20people%20with%20neurodiversity%20get%20jobs.%20She%20has%20helped%20over%2050%20people%20secure%20jobs%20and%20raised%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20for%20neurodivergent%20artists%20by%20showcasing%20their%20artwork.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325345%2Fdelhi-tarini-malhotra-started-nai-subah-foundation-ngo-for-neurodivergent-community-get-jobs%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Pics%3A%2012%20Rare%20%26%20Stunning%20Shots%20Captured%20By%20Wildlife%20Photographers%20Across%20the%20World%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETowards%20the%2029%20and%2030%20of%20this%20month%2C%20hundreds%20of%20wildlife%20photographers%20will%20gather%20at%20the%20Jayamahal%20Palace%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Armed%20with%20shots%20that%20could%20make%20it%20to%20the%20front%20covers%20of%20the%20most%20acclaimed%20magazines%2C%20they%20will%20discuss%20wildlife%20conservation%2C%20share%20their%20observations%20on%20potential%20policies%2C%20and%20ideate%20on%20how%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297656%2Fias-officer-dr-m-k-ranjitsinh-behind-cheetah-relocation-project-india-kuno-national-park%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escope%20of%20wildlife%20protection%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20be%20scaled%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20is%20one%20of%20the%20many%20under%20the%20umbrella%20of%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20media%20and%20production%20house%20Nature%20inFocus%20incepted%20by%20friends%20and%20wildlife%20enthusiasts%20Rohit%20Varma%20(50)%20and%20Kalyan%20Varma%20(43).%20It%20all%20began%20when%20Rohit%20%E2%80%94%20a%20marketing%20professional%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Kalyan%20%E2%80%94%20an%20engineer%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%94%20were%20introduced%20during%20a%20photography%20expedition%20in%202011.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20felt%20there%20was%20no%20single%20platform%20where%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C