0are%20two%20main%20issues%20%E2%80%94%20spatial%20resolution%20and%20spectral%20resolution.%20As%20farm%20sizes%20increase%20and%20we%20move%20into%20the%20age%20of%20automation%2C%20technology%20is%20going%20to%20need%20to%20fill%20the%20gap%20of%20determining%20crop%20issues%20earlier.%20And%20this%20is%20where%20hyperspectral%20data%20and%20parallel%20research%20come%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tim%20Neale%2C%20Managing%20Director%20at%20DataFarming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPixxel%20has%20launched%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323066%2Fchandrayaan-3-the-history-of-how-india-began-one-of-its-most-significant-space-journeys%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethree%20satellites%20%3C%2Fa%3Eso%20far%20and%20is%20gearing%20up%20to%20launch%20six%20more%20early%20next%20year.%20In%20April%202022%2C%20it%20launched%20%E2%80%98Shakuntala%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20SpaceX%20Falcon-9%20rocket%2C%20becoming%20one%20of%20the%20first%20Indian%20companies%20to%20launch%20a%20commercial%20satellite.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202022%2C%20Pixxel%20launched%20it%E2%80%99s%20third%20hyperspectral%20satellite%20%E2%80%98Anand%E2%80%99%20on%20an%20ISRO%20PSLV-C54%20rocket.%20Anand%20is%20a%2015%20kg%20satellite%20that%20will%20view%20our%20planet%20in%20detail%20and%20provide%20environmental%20data%20through%20more%20than%20150%20wavelengths.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOvercoming%20funding%20challenges%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpixxel5-1689934896.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pixxel's%20team%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpixxel5-1689934896.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebe